WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:46.212
http://subscene.com/u/659433
Improved by: @Ivandrofly

00:46.214 --> 00:49.467
<font color="#808080">(CELTIC FLUTE MUSIC PLAYING)</font>

01:10.488 --> 01:11.906
<font color="#808080">(BIRDSONG)</font>

01:18.788 --> 01:22.308
Where are you?
Come out!

01:22.333 --> 01:24.419
Come out!
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font>

01:25.295 --> 01:27.313
Come on out.

01:27.338 --> 01:28.648
<font color="#808080">(GIGGLES)</font>

01:28.673 --> 01:32.343
- I'm coming to get you.
- <font color="#808080">(GIGGLES)</font>

01:33.636 --> 01:36.698
Where are you, you little
rascal? I'm coming to get you.

01:36.723 --> 01:38.742
Hm.
<font color="#808080">(CHUCKLES)</font>

01:38.767 --> 01:41.478
Where is my little
birthday girl, hm?

01:42.353 --> 01:45.665
I'm going to gobble her
up when I find her.

01:45.690 --> 01:47.542
- Oh! <font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font>
<font color="#808080">(SQUEALS)</font>

01:47.567 --> 01:49.586
I'm going to eat you.
I am.

01:49.611 --> 01:51.629
<font color="#808080">(MAKES MUNCHING NOISES)</font>

01:51.654 --> 01:55.175
Och, Fergus, no
weapons on the table.

01:55.200 --> 01:57.469
Can I shoot an arrow? Can I?
Can I? Can I? Can I?

01:57.494 --> 01:59.763
Please? Can I?
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font>

01:59.788 --> 02:02.849
- Not with that. Why not...
- <font color="#808080">(GIGGLES)</font>

02:02.874 --> 02:04.267
use your very own?

02:04.292 --> 02:07.587
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>
- Happy Birthday, my wee darling!

02:08.213 --> 02:09.214
<font color="#808080">(BOW BEING PLUCKED)</font>

02:11.466 --> 02:13.568
- Now, there's a good girl.
- <font color="#808080">(STRAINS)</font>

02:13.593 --> 02:16.179
Draw all the way back now to
your cheek. That's right.

02:17.472 --> 02:19.474
Keep both eyes open.

02:20.433 --> 02:22.435
And, loose!

02:24.562 --> 02:26.564
- I missed.
- Go and fetch it, then.

02:28.900 --> 02:31.861
A bow, Fergus?
She's a lady.

02:32.112 --> 02:33.988
- Ooh! You!
- <font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font>

02:42.372 --> 02:44.666
<font color="#808080">(BIRDS CALLING)</font>

02:57.512 --> 02:59.514
<font color="#808080">(CREAKING)</font>

03:01.724 --> 03:03.601
<font color="#808080">(LONE BIRD CALLS)</font>

03:04.435 --> 03:06.271
<font color="#808080">(HEAVY BREATHING)</font>

03:08.189 --> 03:10.191
<font color="#808080">(HIGH-PITCHED CALL)</font>

03:11.401 --> 03:12.443
A will-o-the-wisp.

03:15.113 --> 03:16.698
<font color="#808080">(GROWLING)</font>

03:20.743 --> 03:22.871
They are real.

03:30.837 --> 03:33.481
<font color="#0080FF">ELINOR</font>: Merida, come
along, sweetheart.

03:33.506 --> 03:35.675
- We're leaving now.
- <font color="#0080FF">MERIDA</font>: I saw a wisp.

03:37.677 --> 03:39.821
- I saw a wisp.
- A wisp?

03:39.846 --> 03:45.243
You know, some say that
will-o-the-wisps lead you to your fate.

03:45.268 --> 03:47.787
- Oh, aye. Or an arrow.
- Och!

03:47.812 --> 03:50.874
Come on, let's be off before
we see a dancing Tatty Bogle.

03:50.899 --> 03:53.376
Or a giant having a
jigger in the bluebells.

03:53.401 --> 03:55.336
Your father doesn't
believe in magic.

03:55.361 --> 03:57.839
Well, he should.
Because it's true.

03:57.864 --> 03:59.299
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

03:59.324 --> 04:00.800
<font color="#808080">(GROWLS)</font>

04:00.825 --> 04:02.594
Mor'du! Elinor, run!

04:02.619 --> 04:04.637
<font color="#808080">(ROARS)</font>
- Sire!

04:04.662 --> 04:06.664
<font color="#808080">(YELLS)</font>

04:09.792 --> 04:11.792
<font color="#808080">(SNARLS)</font>

04:13.254 --> 04:14.397
Come on, you!

04:14.422 --> 04:16.422
<font color="#808080">(ROARS)</font>

04:27.852 --> 04:30.980
<font color="#0080FF">MERIDA</font>: <i> Some say our destiny
is tied to the land...</i>

04:32.023 --> 04:34.525
<i>as much a pan' of
us as we are of it.</i>

04:37.862 --> 04:41.758
<i>Others say fate is woven
together like a cloth.</i>

04:41.783 --> 04:43.301
<font color="#808080">(THUNDER RUMBLES)</font>

04:43.326 --> 04:46.537
<i>So that one's destiny
intertwines with many others.</i>

04:50.750 --> 04:55.546
<i>It's the one thing we search
for or fight to change.</i>

04:57.340 --> 04:59.342
<i>Some never find it.</i>

05:01.594 --> 05:04.722
<i>But there are
some who are led.</i>

05:09.644 --> 05:10.703
<font color="#808080">(YELLS)</font>

05:10.728 --> 05:12.480
<i>The story of how my
father lost his leg</i>

05:13.564 --> 05:15.084
<i>to the demon bear
Mor'du became legend.</i>

05:16.150 --> 05:17.318
<font color="#808080">(GROANING)</font>

05:18.319 --> 05:20.880
<i>I became a sister to
three new brothers.</i>

05:20.905 --> 05:23.908
<i>The princes. Hamish,
Hubert and Harris.</i>

05:24.575 --> 05:26.970
<i>Wee devils, more like.</i>

05:26.995 --> 05:29.555
<i>They get away with murder.</i>

05:29.580 --> 05:31.833
<i>I can never get
away with anything.</i>

05:33.793 --> 05:35.895
<i>I'm the Princess.</i>

05:35.920 --> 05:37.563
- Oh!
- <font color="#808080">(BAGPIPES PLAYING)</font>

05:37.588 --> 05:39.590
<font color="#0080FF">MERIDA</font>: <i> I'm the example.</i>

05:40.550 --> 05:41.609
<font color="#808080">(SLURPS)</font>

05:41.634 --> 05:44.654
<i>I've got duties,
responsibilities, expectations.</i>

05:44.679 --> 05:46.531
<i>My whole life is planned out,</i>

05:46.556 --> 05:48.574
<i>preparing for the
day I become...</i>

05:48.599 --> 05:50.076
<i>Well, my mother.</i>

05:50.101 --> 05:52.996
<i>She's in charge of every
single day of my life.</i>

05:53.021 --> 05:55.023
<font color="#808080">(BAGPIPES CEASE)</font>
<font color="#808080">(SIGHS)</font>

05:56.399 --> 05:59.919
<i>"Aye, Robin, Jolly Robin, and
thou shalt know of mine."</i>

05:59.944 --> 06:01.070
Project!

06:01.320 --> 06:03.072
<i>"And thou shalt know of mine!"</i>

06:03.322 --> 06:06.759
Enunciate. You must be understood
from anywhere in the room,

06:06.784 --> 06:08.428
or it's all for naught.

06:08.453 --> 06:11.014
- This is all for naught.
- I heard that!

06:11.039 --> 06:12.598
<font color="#808080">(SIGHS)</font>
- From the top.

06:12.623 --> 06:15.585
A Princess must be knowledgeable
about her kingdom.

06:17.128 --> 06:19.130
She does not doodle.

06:19.672 --> 06:21.733
<font color="#808080">(PLAYS NOTES)</font>

06:21.758 --> 06:23.760
That's a C, dear.

06:26.429 --> 06:28.614
<font color="#808080">(SCREECHES)</font>
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

06:28.639 --> 06:30.450
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHS AND SNORTS)</font>

06:30.475 --> 06:32.618
A Princess does not chortle.

06:32.643 --> 06:34.746
- Mm!
- Does not stuff her gob!

06:34.771 --> 06:36.539
Rises early.

06:36.564 --> 06:38.416
- Is compassionate...
- <font color="#808080">(CHICKEN SQUAWKS)</font>

06:38.441 --> 06:39.917
patient, cautious,

06:39.942 --> 06:40.960
clean.

06:40.985 --> 06:47.992
And above all, a Princess strives
for... Well, perfection.

06:49.619 --> 06:51.162
<font color="#0080FF">MERIDA</font>: <i> But every
once in a while,</i>

06:51.412 --> 06:56.000
<i>there's a day when I don't
have to be a Princess.</i>

06:58.628 --> 07:01.147
<i>No lessons, no expectations.</i>

07:01.172 --> 07:03.508
<i>A day where anything
can happen.</i>

07:05.093 --> 07:08.154
<i>A day I can change my fate.</i>

07:08.179 --> 07:09.388
Yeah!

07:18.022 --> 07:20.024
<font color="#808080">(LIVELY MUSIC PLAYING)</font>

07:20.233 --> 07:26.297
<i>When cold wind is a' calling, and
the sky is clear and bright.</i>

07:26.322 --> 07:31.994
<i>Misty mountains sing and beckon,
lead me out into the light.</i>

07:32.370 --> 07:35.348
<i>I will ride, I will fly.</i>

07:35.373 --> 07:38.392
<i>Chase the wind and
touch the sky.</i>

07:38.417 --> 07:44.090
<i>I will fly Chase the
wind and touch the sky.</i>

07:49.220 --> 07:51.222
Wooh-hoo!

07:58.396 --> 07:59.539
<font color="#808080">(EAGLE CALLS)</font>

07:59.564 --> 08:05.628
<i>Where dark woods hide secrets and
mountains are fierce and bold.</i>

08:05.653 --> 08:11.676
<i>Deep waters hold reflections
of times lost long ago.</i>

08:11.701 --> 08:15.721
<i>I will read every story,
take hold of my own dream.</i>

08:15.746 --> 08:17.765
- Oh!
- <font color="#808080">(HORSE WHINNIES)</font>

08:17.790 --> 08:20.935
<i>Be as strong as the
seas are Stormy.</i>

08:20.960 --> 08:23.771
<i>And proud as an
eagle's scream.</i>

08:23.796 --> 08:26.816
<i>I will ride, I will fly.</i>

08:26.841 --> 08:29.819
<i>Chase the wind and
touch the sky.</i>

08:29.844 --> 08:35.600
<i>I will fly Chase the
wind and touch the sky</i>

08:44.192 --> 08:46.252
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS EXCITEDLY)</font>

08:46.277 --> 08:48.171
<i>And touch the sky.</i>

08:48.196 --> 08:50.198
Wooh!

08:51.991 --> 08:53.467
<i>Chase the wind.</i>

08:53.492 --> 08:56.554
<i>Chase the wind.</i>

08:56.579 --> 09:01.751
<i>Touch the sky</i>

09:09.008 --> 09:10.193
<font color="#808080">(WHINNIES)</font>

09:10.218 --> 09:13.512
I'm starving. You
hungry too, Angus?

09:13.971 --> 09:15.031
Pfft!

09:15.056 --> 09:17.016
- Oats it is, then.
- <font color="#808080">(SNORTS)</font>

09:19.227 --> 09:20.953
Good day, Princess.

09:20.978 --> 09:22.914
I cannot find the salt.
Where did you put it?

09:22.939 --> 09:25.339
It was over there a minute ago,
the last time I looked at it.

09:25.942 --> 09:30.963
And then, out of nowhere, the
biggest bear you've ever seen!

09:30.988 --> 09:34.175
His hide littered with the
weapons of fallen warriors.

09:34.200 --> 09:37.828
His face scarred
with one dead eye.

09:38.621 --> 09:40.306
I drew my sword and...

09:40.331 --> 09:41.933
Whoosh!

09:41.958 --> 09:44.143
One swipe, his sword shattered.

09:44.168 --> 09:47.296
Then "chomp"!
Dad's leg was clean off.

09:47.672 --> 09:50.107
Down the monster's
throat it went.

09:50.132 --> 09:53.110
Oh, that's my favorite part.

09:53.135 --> 09:56.389
Mor'du has never
been seen since,

09:56.514 --> 10:01.994
and is roaming the wilds
waiting his chance of revenge.

10:02.019 --> 10:04.580
<font color="#808080">(ROARING)</font>
- Let him return.

10:04.605 --> 10:06.707
I'll finish what I guddled
in the first place.

10:06.732 --> 10:10.586
Merida, a Princess does not
place her weapons on the table.

10:10.611 --> 10:13.839
Mum!
It's just my bow.

10:13.864 --> 10:16.884
A Princess should not have
weapons in my opinion.

10:16.909 --> 10:18.244
<font color="#0080FF">FERGUS</font>: Leave her be.

10:18.536 --> 10:21.264
Princess or not, learning
to fight is essential.

10:21.289 --> 10:24.141
Mum? You'll never guess
what I did today.

10:24.166 --> 10:26.335
- Hm?
- I climbed the Crone's Tooth,

10:26.585 --> 10:27.878
and drank from the Fire Falls.

10:28.421 --> 10:29.855
Fire Falls?

10:29.880 --> 10:33.693
They say only the ancient kings were
brave enough to drink the fire.

10:33.718 --> 10:34.777
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font>

10:34.802 --> 10:37.655
- What did you do, dear?
- Nothing, Mum.

10:37.680 --> 10:39.198
Hungry, aren't we?

10:39.223 --> 10:41.659
- Mum!
- You'll get dreadful collywobbles.

10:41.684 --> 10:44.704
Oh, Fergus, will you look
at your daughter's plate?

10:44.729 --> 10:46.747
<font color="#808080">(DOGS BARKING)</font>
- So what?

10:46.772 --> 10:49.333
- Oh, you great...
- Don't let them lick... <font color="#808080">(SIGHS)</font>

10:49.358 --> 10:50.710
Boys, you're naughty.

10:50.735 --> 10:52.820
Don't just play
with your haggis.

10:53.070 --> 10:55.881
- Urgh! <font color="#808080">(GAGGING)</font>
- Och, how do you know you don't like it,

10:55.906 --> 10:58.050
if you won't try it?

10:58.075 --> 10:59.969
That's just a wee
sheep's stomach.

10:59.994 --> 11:02.680
It's delicious. Mm!
<font color="#808080">(SMACKS LIPS)</font>

11:02.705 --> 11:05.057
- My lady.
- Thank you, Maudie.

11:05.082 --> 11:08.082
<font color="#0080FF">FERGUS</font>: You're getting
too big, the two of you.

11:10.963 --> 11:12.315
<font color="#0080FF">ELINOR</font>: Aha.

11:12.340 --> 11:14.734
From the Lords Macintosh,
MacGuffin and Dingwall.

11:14.759 --> 11:16.193
Their responses, no doubt.

11:16.218 --> 11:17.778
Aye, aye!

11:17.803 --> 11:19.805
<font color="#0080FF">FERGUS</font>: Hey, hey!
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font> <font color="#808080">(MUNCHING LOUDLY)</font>

11:20.681 --> 11:23.351
Stay out of my food,
you greedy mongrels.

11:24.018 --> 11:26.203
Chew on that, you manky dogs!

11:26.228 --> 11:28.272
<font color="#808080">(FERGUS LAUGHS)</font>
- Fergus?

11:30.816 --> 11:32.084
They've all accepted.

11:32.109 --> 11:34.111
<font color="#808080">(DOGS SLOBBERING)</font>

11:34.779 --> 11:37.048
Who's accepted what, Mother?

11:37.073 --> 11:39.283
Boys, you are excused.

11:39.992 --> 11:41.035
<font color="#808080">(GIGGLING)</font>

11:42.119 --> 11:43.245
- Oof!
- <font color="#808080">(DOGS BARKING)</font>

11:43.913 --> 11:45.206
Hey!
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font>

11:46.165 --> 11:49.060
What did I do now?

11:49.085 --> 11:51.295
Your father has something
to discuss with you.

11:53.798 --> 11:54.965
Fergus?

11:55.800 --> 11:57.735
Oh.
<font color="#808080">(CLEARS THROAT)</font>

11:57.760 --> 11:59.428
<font color="#808080">(COUGHS)</font>

11:59.678 --> 12:02.890
Er... Merida.

12:05.935 --> 12:11.123
<font color="#808080">(SIGHS)</font> The lords are presenting their
sons as suitors for your betrothal.

12:11.148 --> 12:13.984
- What?
- The clans have accepted.

12:14.652 --> 12:17.171
- Dad!
- What? <font color="#808080">(STAMMERS)</font> I...

12:17.196 --> 12:19.423
You... She... Elinor?

12:19.448 --> 12:22.093
Honestly, Merida, I don't know
why you're reacting this way.

12:22.118 --> 12:23.135
<font color="#808080">(SIGHS IN FRUSTRATION)</font>

12:23.160 --> 12:27.181
This year, each clan will present a suitor
to compete in the games for your hand.

12:27.206 --> 12:29.975
I suppose a Princess just
does what she's told?

12:30.000 --> 12:32.420
A Princess does not
raise her voice.

12:33.254 --> 12:36.298
Merida, this is what you've been
preparing for your whole life.

12:36.841 --> 12:40.319
No, it's what you've been
preparing me for my whole life.

12:40.344 --> 12:42.738
I won't go through with it.
You can't make me.

12:42.763 --> 12:44.890
Merida!

12:45.099 --> 12:46.934
Huh? Merida!

12:49.687 --> 12:50.746
- Urgh!
- <font color="#808080">(DOGS BARKING)</font>

12:50.771 --> 12:53.023
Boys!

12:53.983 --> 12:55.985
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTING)</font>

12:57.194 --> 13:00.965
Mother. Suitors? Marriage?

13:00.990 --> 13:03.384
Once there was an
ancient kingdom...

13:03.409 --> 13:06.095
Oh, Mum!

13:06.120 --> 13:07.805
Ancient kingdom.

13:07.830 --> 13:09.874
It's name long forgotten,

13:10.458 --> 13:14.462
ruled by a wise and fair
King who was much beloved.

13:14.962 --> 13:20.025
And when he grew old he divided
the kingdom among his four sons,

13:20.050 --> 13:24.430
that they should be the pillars on
which the peace of the land rested.

13:25.806 --> 13:30.870
But the oldest Prince wanted
to rule the land for himself.

13:30.895 --> 13:34.482
He followed his own path
and the kingdom fell

13:35.774 --> 13:38.794
to war, and chaos and ruin.

13:38.819 --> 13:40.796
That's a nice story.

13:40.821 --> 13:43.132
It's not just a story, Merida.

13:43.157 --> 13:46.260
Legends are lessons.
They ring with truths.

13:46.285 --> 13:47.803
Och, Mum.

13:47.828 --> 13:50.055
I would advise you to make
your peace with this.

13:50.080 --> 13:51.974
The clans are coming to
present their suitors.

13:51.999 --> 13:54.393
- It's not fair.
- Och, Merida.

13:54.418 --> 13:57.171
It's marriage. It's not
the end of the world.

13:58.255 --> 13:59.256
<font color="#808080">(SIGHS IN DISBELIEF)</font>

14:01.217 --> 14:03.219
<font color="#808080">(ELINOR MUTTERING)</font>

14:05.930 --> 14:08.641
<font color="#0080FF">FERGUS</font>: - You're muttering.
- I don't mutter.

14:09.266 --> 14:12.561
Aye, you do. You mutter, lass,
when something's troubling you.

14:12.811 --> 14:14.914
I blame you. Stubbornness.

14:14.939 --> 14:16.624
It's entirely from your
side of the family.

14:16.649 --> 14:19.527
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font> I take it the talk
didn't go too well, then?

14:20.110 --> 14:22.171
Ooh, I don't know what to do.

14:22.196 --> 14:25.257
- Speak to her, dear.
- I do speak to her.

14:25.282 --> 14:28.577
- She just doesn't listen.
- Come on, now.

14:28.827 --> 14:31.263
Pretend I'm Merida.
Speak to me.

14:31.288 --> 14:33.265
What would you say?

14:33.290 --> 14:35.851
Ooh... I can't do this.

14:35.876 --> 14:37.520
Sure you can.

14:37.545 --> 14:40.189
There, there.
That's my Queen.

14:40.214 --> 14:42.233
Right, here we go.

14:42.258 --> 14:44.026
"I don't want to get married."

14:44.051 --> 14:46.570
"I want to stay single and let
my hair flow in the wind"

14:46.595 --> 14:50.516
"as I ride through the Glen
firing arrows into the sunset."

14:53.477 --> 14:55.913
<font color="#808080">(BREATHES DEEPLY)</font>

14:55.938 --> 15:00.960
Merida, all this work, all the
time spent preparing you,

15:00.985 --> 15:04.613
schooling you, giving you
everything we never had.

15:04.863 --> 15:08.384
I ask you, what do
you expect us to do?

15:08.409 --> 15:11.554
Call off the gathering.
Would that kill them?

15:11.579 --> 15:12.972
You're the Queen.

15:12.997 --> 15:16.350
You can just tell the lords the
Princess is not ready for this.

15:16.375 --> 15:20.104
In fact, she might not ever be
ready for this, so that's that.

15:20.129 --> 15:24.233
Good day to you. We'll expect your
declarations of war in the morning.

15:24.258 --> 15:27.987
I understand this
must all seem unfair.

15:28.012 --> 15:30.364
Even I had reservations
when I faced betrothal.

15:30.389 --> 15:33.951
But we can't just run
away from who we are.

15:33.976 --> 15:36.495
I don't want my life to be over.

15:36.520 --> 15:37.997
I want my freedom!

15:38.022 --> 15:41.333
But are you willing to pay the
price your freedom will cost?

15:41.358 --> 15:43.502
I'm not doing any of
this to hurt you.

15:43.527 --> 15:49.133
If you could just try to see
what I do, I do out of love.

15:49.158 --> 15:52.119
But it's my life, it's...
<font color="#808080">(SIGHS)</font>

15:52.536 --> 15:54.346
I'm just not ready.

15:54.371 --> 15:56.307
I think you'd see,
if you could just...

15:56.332 --> 15:59.435
I think I could make you
understand if you would just...

15:59.460 --> 16:01.103
- listen.
- Listen.

16:01.128 --> 16:02.463
<font color="#808080">(WHINNIES)</font>

16:04.381 --> 16:07.551
I swear, Angus, this
isn't going to happen.

16:08.552 --> 16:10.179
Not if I have any say in it.

16:12.097 --> 16:14.725
<font color="#808080">(EXERTIVE GRUNTING)</font>
<font color="#808080">(DRUMS POUNDING)</font>

16:16.977 --> 16:18.312
<font color="#808080">(MEN STRAINING)</font>

16:22.316 --> 16:24.318
<font color="#808080">(DRUMS BEATING RHYTHMICALLY)</font>

16:26.904 --> 16:28.547
MacGuffin!

16:28.572 --> 16:30.074
<font color="#0080FF">MEN</font>: MacGuffin!

16:32.993 --> 16:34.995
- Dingwall!
<font color="#0080FF">MEN</font>: - Dingwall!

16:36.705 --> 16:39.625
- Macintosh!
<font color="#0080FF">MEN</font>: - Macintosh!

16:45.422 --> 16:47.424
Ooh! Aah!

16:48.008 --> 16:49.009
Oh.

16:50.302 --> 16:51.303
<font color="#808080">(SIGHS)</font>

16:51.595 --> 16:52.613
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTS)</font>

16:52.638 --> 16:56.158
You look absolutely beautiful.

16:56.183 --> 16:57.534
I can't breathe.

16:57.559 --> 16:59.561
Och, shush!
Give us a turn.

17:01.021 --> 17:03.374
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>
I can't move.

17:03.399 --> 17:05.501
It's too tight.

17:05.526 --> 17:08.337
<font color="#808080">(STRAINS)</font>
- It's perfect.

17:08.362 --> 17:10.280
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

17:10.948 --> 17:12.616
<font color="#808080">(STRAINS)</font>

17:20.665 --> 17:23.210
- Merida?
- Mum?

17:26.130 --> 17:28.132
Just...

17:30.759 --> 17:33.011
Remember to smile.

17:36.974 --> 17:38.976
<font color="#808080">(SNORING)</font>

17:42.104 --> 17:44.106
<font color="#808080">(PRINCES LAUGHING)</font>

17:46.567 --> 17:48.544
<font color="#808080">(CONTINUES SNORING)</font>
- Aye, they're coming.

17:48.569 --> 17:50.921
Places, everyone. Places.

17:50.946 --> 17:52.448
<font color="#808080">(PEOPLE CLAMORING)</font>
<font color="#808080">(DOGS BARKING)</font>

17:52.948 --> 17:54.950
Oh!

18:03.417 --> 18:05.419
<font color="#808080">(PRINCES GRUNTING)</font>

18:05.711 --> 18:07.730
<font color="#808080">(FERGUS CHUCKLES)</font>

18:07.755 --> 18:10.340
I look fine, woman! Leave me be!

18:10.674 --> 18:12.067
<font color="#0080FF">GUARD</font>: My Lord!

18:12.092 --> 18:15.362
I want to announce the
arrival of the lords...

18:15.387 --> 18:17.489
- Ow!
- Who goes there? Who goes there?

18:17.514 --> 18:19.516
<font color="#808080">(BAGPIPES PLAYING)</font>

18:34.156 --> 18:36.158
Boy!

18:36.825 --> 18:39.136
<font color="#808080">(ALL CRY OUT)</font>

18:39.161 --> 18:40.746
<font color="#808080">(SHOUTING)</font>

18:44.374 --> 18:45.375
<font color="#808080">(SILENCE)</font>

18:46.335 --> 18:49.254
So, here we are... Er...

18:50.047 --> 18:52.274
the four clans.
<font color="#0080FF">MAN</font>: - Aye.

18:52.299 --> 18:54.301
- Er... Gathering...
- Oh.

18:55.093 --> 18:57.279
- For...
- <font color="#808080">(DISCONTENTED MURMURS)</font>

18:57.304 --> 19:00.849
- the presentation of the suitors.
- The presentation of the suitors.

19:01.099 --> 19:03.702
<font color="#808080">(ALL CHEERING)</font>
<font color="#0080FF">FERGUS</font>: - Clan Macintosh.

19:03.727 --> 19:06.121
<font color="#0080FF">MEN</font>: Macintosh!

19:06.146 --> 19:09.708
Your Majesty, I present
my heir and scion,

19:09.733 --> 19:13.295
who defended our land from
the northern invaders,

19:13.320 --> 19:17.549
and with his own
sword, Stab Blooder,

19:17.574 --> 19:19.760
vanquished 1,000 foes.

19:19.785 --> 19:21.787
<font color="#0080FF">MEN</font>: Macintosh!

19:23.038 --> 19:25.057
<font color="#808080">(SCOFFS)</font>
<font color="#0080FF">FERGUS</font>: - Clan MacGuffin!

19:25.082 --> 19:26.750
<font color="#0080FF">MEN</font>: MacGuffin!

19:27.543 --> 19:31.814
Good Majesty, I present
my eldest son,

19:31.839 --> 19:34.691
who scuttled the
Viking longships

19:34.716 --> 19:39.429
and with his bare hands
vanquished 2,000 foes.

19:39.680 --> 19:41.682
<font color="#0080FF">MEN</font>: MacGuffin!

19:44.434 --> 19:45.744
Clan Dingwall.

19:45.769 --> 19:47.771
<font color="#0080FF">MEN</font>: Dingwall!

19:48.856 --> 19:51.942
I present my only son

19:53.443 --> 19:57.589
who was besieged
by 10,000 Romans

19:57.614 --> 20:01.869
and he took out a whole
armada singlehandedly.

20:01.994 --> 20:03.453
With one arm, he was...

20:04.746 --> 20:07.474
With one arm he was
steering the ship

20:07.499 --> 20:10.686
and with the other he
held his mighty sword

20:10.711 --> 20:13.480
and struck down a whole
attacking fleet.

20:13.505 --> 20:15.883
<font color="#0080FF">MAN</font>: - Lies!
- What? I heard that.

20:16.133 --> 20:18.135
<font color="#808080">(MEN SNICKERING)</font>
- Go on. Say it to my face.

20:18.468 --> 20:21.196
Or are ye scared,
simpering jackanapes,

20:21.221 --> 20:23.574
afraid to muss your pretty hair?

20:23.599 --> 20:26.785
- At least we have hair.
- And all our teeth.

20:26.810 --> 20:29.454
<font color="#808080">(SPEAKS IN THICK ACCENT)</font>

20:29.479 --> 20:31.290
<font color="#0080FF">MAN</font>: - Huh?
<font color="#808080">(SHEEP BLEATS)</font>

20:31.315 --> 20:34.835
And we don't hide under
Bridges, you grumpy old troll.

20:34.860 --> 20:36.820
<font color="#808080">(ALL LAUGHING)</font>

20:38.322 --> 20:40.449
You want to laugh, huh?

20:40.741 --> 20:42.659
Wee Dingwall!

20:43.827 --> 20:45.954
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>
Get off me!

20:46.204 --> 20:47.639
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHING)</font>

20:47.664 --> 20:48.724
<font color="#808080">(PLAYING LIVELY TUNE)</font>

20:48.749 --> 20:50.125
<font color="#808080">(GROANING)</font>

20:53.754 --> 20:54.755
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

20:55.839 --> 20:57.691
<font color="#808080">(YELPS)</font>

20:57.716 --> 21:00.177
Nut them! Nut them!
That's the way to...

21:02.387 --> 21:03.555
Alright.

21:05.474 --> 21:06.892
Shut it!

21:07.517 --> 21:08.685
<font color="#808080">(MUSIC WINDS DOWN)</font>

21:09.227 --> 21:13.941
Now, that's all done. You've
had your go at each other.

21:14.191 --> 21:15.859
Show a little decorum.

21:16.902 --> 21:18.946
And no more fighting.

21:19.196 --> 21:20.505
<font color="#808080">(MACE CLANGING)</font>
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

21:20.530 --> 21:21.531
<font color="#808080">(LIVELY TUNE CONTINUES)</font>

21:22.199 --> 21:23.200
<font color="#808080">(YELLING)</font>

21:29.706 --> 21:31.375
<font color="#808080">(BATTLE CRY)</font>

21:33.543 --> 21:34.544
Ow!

21:35.671 --> 21:36.672
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

21:37.506 --> 21:39.299
<font color="#808080">(SHEEP BLEATS)</font>

21:39.758 --> 21:40.759
<font color="#808080">(YELLS)</font>

21:52.270 --> 21:54.272
<font color="#0080FF">FERGUS</font>: You want a fresh one?

21:54.523 --> 21:56.333
<font color="#808080">(MUSIC STOPS)</font>

21:56.358 --> 21:58.360
<font color="#808080">(CLAN CHIEFS WHINING IN PAIN)</font>

22:00.305 --> 22:01.505
<font color="#0080FF">FERGUS</font>: Crivens,
you're fierce.

22:01.530 --> 22:02.923
I didn't start it. It was...

22:02.948 --> 22:05.676
My lady Queen, I feel terrible.
My humblest apologies.

22:05.701 --> 22:09.346
- We mean no disrespect.
- I'm sorry, love, I didn't... But...

22:09.371 --> 22:11.556
- Yes, dear.
- <font color="#808080">(CLEARS THROAT)</font>

22:11.581 --> 22:13.392
Now, where were we?

22:13.417 --> 22:17.045
Ah, yes.
In accordance with our laws,

22:17.295 --> 22:19.690
by the rights of our heritage,

22:19.715 --> 22:23.026
only the firstborn of
each of the great leaders

22:23.051 --> 22:25.946
- may be presented as champion.
- Firstborn?

22:25.971 --> 22:30.684
And thus compete for the hand
of the Princess of Dun Broch.

22:31.268 --> 22:34.621
To win the fair maiden they
must prove their worth

22:34.646 --> 22:38.875
by feats of strength
or arms in the games.

22:38.900 --> 22:43.588
It is customary that the challenge be
determined by the Princess herself.

22:43.613 --> 22:45.382
Archery!
Archery.

22:45.407 --> 22:46.616
<font color="#808080">(ALL MURMURING)</font>

22:47.784 --> 22:51.580
I choose archery.

22:52.330 --> 22:55.500
- Let the games begin!
- <font color="#808080">(ALL CHEERING)</font>

23:05.010 --> 23:07.471
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTING)</font>
<font color="#808080">(YELLS)</font>

23:11.391 --> 23:12.451
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

23:12.476 --> 23:13.477
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTING)</font>

23:15.812 --> 23:17.397
Pull!

23:18.023 --> 23:19.858
- Pull!
- <font color="#808080">(MEN CRYING OUT IN SURPRISE)</font>

23:19.983 --> 23:21.651
<font color="#808080">(LIVELY BAGPIPES PLAYING)</font>

23:27.574 --> 23:29.576
<font color="#808080">(MAN ROARING)</font>
<font color="#808080">(CHILDREN SCREAMING)</font>

23:32.954 --> 23:34.956
<font color="#808080">(MOOING AND BARKING)</font>

23:36.583 --> 23:38.335
- I'll just take one.
- Ooh!

23:39.586 --> 23:41.588
<font color="#0080FF">PRINCE</font>: Ooh!

23:43.131 --> 23:44.775
Oh!

23:44.800 --> 23:48.345
Now, I have told you,
you're not allowed... Oh!

23:49.429 --> 23:50.847
- Oh!
- Argh!

23:51.431 --> 23:53.058
<font color="#808080">(PRINCES GIGGLING)</font>
- Oh!

23:56.103 --> 23:58.021
<font color="#808080">(SHEEP BLEATING)</font>

24:00.899 --> 24:02.901
<font color="#808080">(HORN SOUNDING)</font>

24:04.903 --> 24:07.656
<font color="#808080">(DOGS HOWL)</font>

24:07.781 --> 24:09.449
<font color="#808080">(CROWD CHEERING)</font>

24:09.825 --> 24:11.201
It's time!

24:13.870 --> 24:17.124
- Archers, to your marks!
- Aye, archers, to your marks.

24:17.374 --> 24:20.102
And may the lucky arrow
find it's target.

24:20.127 --> 24:21.753
<font color="#808080">(FERGUS CHUCKLES)</font>

24:26.049 --> 24:28.051
<font color="#808080">(EXCITED SQUEALING)</font>

24:30.387 --> 24:32.097
Oi! Get on with it.

24:38.937 --> 24:40.413
<font color="#0080FF">CROWD</font>: Ooh. <font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font>

24:40.438 --> 24:41.731
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

24:42.524 --> 24:45.752
- Och!
- I bet he wishes he was tossing cabers.

24:45.777 --> 24:48.738
- Or holding up Bridges. <font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font>
- Shh!

24:51.074 --> 24:52.826
<font color="#808080">(GIRLS SQUEAL)</font>

24:53.785 --> 24:54.886
<font color="#0080FF">CROWD</font>: Aw...

24:54.911 --> 24:56.138
<font color="#808080">(YELLS ANGRILY)</font>

24:56.163 --> 24:59.599
At least you hit
the target, son.

24:59.624 --> 25:01.143
<font color="#808080">(CONTINUES YELLING)</font>

25:01.168 --> 25:03.019
Oh, that's attractive.

25:03.044 --> 25:05.046
<font color="#808080">(CONTINUES WAILING)</font>

25:06.756 --> 25:08.900
<font color="#0080FF">MAN</font>: - I got it!
- Good arm.

25:08.925 --> 25:12.070
And such lovely flowing locks.

25:12.095 --> 25:13.722
- Fergus.
- What?

25:15.891 --> 25:17.117
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHTER)</font>

25:17.142 --> 25:18.143
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>

25:22.856 --> 25:24.608
Oh, wee lamb.

25:30.113 --> 25:32.782
Oh, come on!
Shoot, boy!

25:33.992 --> 25:36.052
<font color="#808080">(CROWD CHEERING)</font>
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHS IN TRIUMPH)</font>

25:36.077 --> 25:37.971
Well done, lad! Well done.

25:37.996 --> 25:39.998
<font color="#808080">(STARTS SINGING)</font>

25:41.458 --> 25:43.627
- Feast your eyes!
- <font color="#808080">(CHIEFS SCREAM)</font>

25:44.461 --> 25:47.214
- That's my boy.
- <font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font> <font color="#808080">(GAGGING)</font>

25:47.464 --> 25:50.984
Well, that's just
grand now, isn't it?

25:51.009 --> 25:53.820
- Guess who's coming to dinner?
- Fergus.

25:53.845 --> 25:56.990
By the way, hope you don't
mind being called Lady Ding...

25:57.015 --> 25:59.017
<font color="#808080">(WHINES)</font>

26:04.147 --> 26:06.833
<font color="#808080">(CROWD GASPS)</font>
- I am Merida.

26:06.858 --> 26:10.128
Firstborn descendant
of Clan Dun Broch.

26:10.153 --> 26:13.715
And I'll be shooting
for my own hand.

26:13.740 --> 26:14.866
- Oh!
- <font color="#808080">(CROWD MURMURING)</font>

26:15.825 --> 26:18.203
What are you doing?

26:20.956 --> 26:22.974
Merida!

26:22.999 --> 26:24.876
Curse this dress!

26:25.252 --> 26:27.254
<font color="#808080">(SHOCKED GASPS)</font>

26:31.007 --> 26:32.050
<font color="#808080">(CROWD GASPS IN AWE)</font>

26:32.175 --> 26:33.718
Merida, stop this!

26:38.014 --> 26:40.850
Don't you dare loose
another arrow.

26:47.857 --> 26:48.942
<font color="#808080">(EXHALES)</font>

26:50.110 --> 26:52.279
Merida, I forbid it.

27:23.059 --> 27:25.745
Michty me! I've just about
had enough of you, lass!

27:25.770 --> 27:28.540
- You're the one that wants me to...
- You embarrassed them.

27:28.565 --> 27:30.458
- You embarrassed me.
- I followed the rules.

27:30.483 --> 27:32.419
You don't know what you've done!

27:32.444 --> 27:35.088
- Just don't care how I...
- It'll be fire and sword if it's not set right.

27:35.113 --> 27:37.716
- Just listen!
- I am the Queen!

27:37.741 --> 27:39.342
You listen to me!

27:39.367 --> 27:41.720
Ugh!
This is so unfair!

27:41.745 --> 27:43.513
Ha! Unfair?

27:43.538 --> 27:45.640
You're never there for me.

27:45.665 --> 27:48.393
This whole marriage
is what you want.

27:48.418 --> 27:51.646
Do you ever bother to
ask what I want? No.

27:51.671 --> 27:54.566
You walk around telling me
what to do, what not to do,

27:54.591 --> 27:57.152
trying to make me be like you.

27:57.177 --> 27:59.529
Well, I'm not going
to be like you.

27:59.554 --> 28:01.281
Oh, you're acting like a child.

28:01.306 --> 28:04.200
And you're a beast.

28:04.225 --> 28:06.202
- That's what you are!
- Oh, Merida.

28:06.227 --> 28:08.621
- I'll never be like you.
- No, stop that!

28:08.646 --> 28:11.649
- I'd rather die than be like you!
- <font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>

28:16.279 --> 28:18.798
Merida, you are a Princess,

28:18.823 --> 28:21.618
- and I expect you to act like one.
- Mum!

28:23.161 --> 28:24.329
Oh!

28:28.958 --> 28:30.018
<font color="#808080">(WEEPS)</font>

28:30.043 --> 28:32.045
<font color="#0080FF">ELINOR</font>: Merida!

28:33.046 --> 28:34.547
Merida!

28:35.465 --> 28:37.442
Oh, dear.

28:37.467 --> 28:39.302
Ah!

28:41.179 --> 28:43.765
Oh, no.
What have I done?

28:45.308 --> 28:46.726
Oh.

28:47.394 --> 28:49.396
<font color="#808080">(SOBBING)</font>

28:54.484 --> 28:56.486
<font color="#808080">(SOBBING)</font>

29:13.128 --> 29:15.422
Oh! Oh! Oh!

29:16.089 --> 29:17.090
<font color="#808080">(WHINNIES)</font>

29:17.674 --> 29:19.818
Whoa!

29:19.843 --> 29:22.220
<font color="#808080">(SOBS)</font>
Angus!

29:22.762 --> 29:25.265
<font color="#808080">(WHINNIES AND SNORTS)</font>

29:34.190 --> 29:36.192
<font color="#808080">(ANGUS WHINNIES)</font>

29:47.328 --> 29:49.372
<font color="#808080">(WISP CALLS)</font>

29:57.672 --> 30:00.216
<font color="#808080">(WISP CALLS)</font>

30:08.558 --> 30:11.619
<font color="#808080">(WHISPERS)</font> Come on, Angus.
<font color="#808080">(ANGUS NICKERS)</font>

30:11.644 --> 30:12.871
Angus!

30:12.896 --> 30:14.539
<font color="#808080">(NICKERS)</font>

30:14.564 --> 30:16.316
<font color="#808080">(SIGHS)</font>

30:16.900 --> 30:18.902
<font color="#808080">(WISPS CALL)</font>

30:20.570 --> 30:22.405
<font color="#808080">(ANGUS NEIGHS)</font>

30:23.573 --> 30:25.700
<font color="#808080">(WISP CALLS)</font>

30:29.537 --> 30:30.663
<font color="#808080">(WHINNYING)</font>

30:55.063 --> 30:57.065
<font color="#808080">(WISP CALLS)</font>

31:01.736 --> 31:04.197
Why would the wisps
lead me here?

31:12.914 --> 31:14.916
<font color="#808080">(BELL TINKLES)</font>

31:15.667 --> 31:16.751
Uh...

31:19.504 --> 31:21.506
<font color="#808080">(WOOD GENTLY TAPPING)</font>

31:29.347 --> 31:31.366
Oh, look around.

31:31.391 --> 31:33.618
You holler if you see
anything you like.

31:33.643 --> 31:35.979
Everything is half off.

31:36.479 --> 31:37.522
Uh...

31:41.359 --> 31:44.462
- Who are you?
- Just a humble woodcarver.

31:44.487 --> 31:45.989
Um...

31:46.281 --> 31:48.841
I don't understand...
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>

31:48.866 --> 31:50.994
- See anything you like?
- Uh...

31:51.286 --> 31:55.431
Perhaps a touch of whimsy to
brighten any dank chamber?

31:55.456 --> 31:57.934
But the will-o-the-wisps,
they...

31:57.959 --> 31:59.961
Oh!
This is one of a kind!

32:00.336 --> 32:02.005
I'll make you a deal
for this rare prize.

32:04.340 --> 32:05.758
- Your broom!
- Oh! <font color="#808080">(SNAPS)</font>

32:07.051 --> 32:10.054
- It was sweeping by itself.
- That's ridiculous.

32:10.346 --> 32:12.907
Wood cannot be imbued
with magical properties.

32:12.932 --> 32:16.494
I should know. I'm a wit...
Whittler.

32:16.519 --> 32:18.329
Of wood.

32:18.354 --> 32:23.668
Oh, how about this conversation
starter? It's made of yew wood.

32:23.693 --> 32:26.087
<font color="#808080">(GENTLE CLATTERING)</font>
- Tough as Stone.

32:26.112 --> 32:27.547
Oh, ah, ah, ah, ah!

32:27.572 --> 32:29.674
That's stuffed.
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font>

32:29.699 --> 32:33.011
- Staring is rude.
- <font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font> Ooh! The crow's talking!

32:33.036 --> 32:34.345
That's not all I can do.

32:34.370 --> 32:36.681
<i>LA-IA LA-LA LA-LA</i>

32:36.706 --> 32:38.583
<font color="#808080">(SINGS HIGH NOTES)</font>
<font color="#808080">(SNAPS)</font>

32:40.877 --> 32:42.503
<font color="#808080">(SQUAWKS)</font>

32:43.046 --> 32:46.024
- You're a witch!
- Woodcarver.

32:46.049 --> 32:48.384
That's why the
wisps led me here.

32:48.885 --> 32:50.987
- Woodcarver!
- You'll change my fate!

32:51.012 --> 32:53.865
- Woodcarver!
- You see, it's my mother.

32:53.890 --> 32:56.976
I'm not a witch! Too many
unsatisfied customers.

32:59.395 --> 33:04.359
If you're not going to buy
anything, get out. <font color="#808080">(SNAPS)</font>

33:04.734 --> 33:07.570
- No! The wisps led me here!
- I don't care!

33:08.738 --> 33:13.326
- Get out! Shoo! Get! Be gone with you!
- <i>I'll</i> buy it all.

33:14.035 --> 33:16.679
- What? What was that?
- Every carving.

33:16.704 --> 33:18.431
Well...
<font color="#808080">(STAMMERING)</font>

33:18.456 --> 33:22.810
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font> And how are you going
to pay for that, sweetie?

33:22.835 --> 33:25.505
- With this.
- W...

33:28.091 --> 33:31.069
Oh, my, that's lovely, that is.

33:31.094 --> 33:32.428
That would set us up for months.

33:32.553 --> 33:33.553
<font color="#808080">(CLATTERING)</font>

33:34.472 --> 33:35.907
<font color="#0080FF">MERIDA</font>: - Ah, ah, ah.
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>

33:35.932 --> 33:41.771
- Every carving and one spell.
- <font color="#808080">(SQUAWKS)</font>

33:42.522 --> 33:45.541
Are you sure you know
what you're doing?

33:45.566 --> 33:49.112
I want a spell to change my mum.

33:49.362 --> 33:51.714
That'll change my fate.

33:51.739 --> 33:53.032
Hmm... Done!

33:54.450 --> 33:55.968
<font color="#808080">(CHUCKLES)</font>
- Where are you going?

33:55.993 --> 33:57.095
<font color="#808080">(SNAPS)</font>

33:57.120 --> 33:58.763
<font color="#808080">(SQUAWKING)</font>
- There.

33:58.788 --> 34:00.123
What are you doing?

34:00.540 --> 34:03.126
You never conjure
where you carve.

34:03.418 --> 34:04.794
Very important.

34:08.547 --> 34:10.983
<font color="#0080FF">WITCH</font>: The last time I did
this was for a Prince.

34:11.007 --> 34:12.610
<font color="#808080">(CLAPS)</font>
<font color="#808080">(CAULDRON IGNITES)</font>

34:12.635 --> 34:14.946
Easy on the eyes.
Tight pants.

34:14.971 --> 34:18.658
He demanded I give him
the strength of ten men.

34:18.683 --> 34:21.936
And he gave me this for a spell.

34:22.728 --> 34:24.688
A spell that would
change his fate.

34:26.607 --> 34:28.083
And did he get
what he was after?

34:28.109 --> 34:29.793
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font>
Yes.

34:29.819 --> 34:33.965
And made off with an especially
attractive mahogany cheese board.

34:33.989 --> 34:36.801
Now, what do I need? Oh!

34:36.826 --> 34:38.928
- Just a little bit of this.
- <font color="#808080">(THUNDER RUMBLING)</font>

34:38.953 --> 34:40.012
Ah.
<font color="#808080">(CHUCKLES)</font>

34:40.036 --> 34:41.038
Hoo!

34:42.081 --> 34:44.641
<font color="#808080">(SQUAWKING)</font>

34:44.667 --> 34:47.061
Tee-tee-tee-tee.
Whoosh.

34:47.085 --> 34:48.838
That'll do.

34:53.176 --> 34:55.178
<font color="#808080">(HUMS HAPPILY)</font>

34:56.637 --> 34:58.848
<font color="#808080">(SQUAWKS)</font>
- Mi-Mi-Mi-Mi-Mi-Mi-Mi.

35:02.059 --> 35:03.119
<font color="#808080">(BANG)</font>

35:03.144 --> 35:04.937
<font color="#808080">(PANICKED WHINNYING)</font>

35:06.564 --> 35:12.695
And now let's see.
What have we here?

35:15.740 --> 35:17.533
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>
oh!

35:18.576 --> 35:19.660
- Hey!
- <font color="#808080">(SQUAWKS)</font>

35:20.703 --> 35:22.597
Uh, a cake?

35:22.622 --> 35:25.625
- You don't want it?
- Yes! I want it.

35:26.167 --> 35:30.254
You're sure if I
give this to my mum,

35:30.546 --> 35:32.256
it will change my fate?

35:32.548 --> 35:34.150
Oh.
<font color="#808080">(CHUCKLES)</font>

35:34.175 --> 35:37.470
Trust me. It'll do
the trick, dearie.

35:38.137 --> 35:43.034
Expect delivery of your
purchase within a fortnight.

35:43.059 --> 35:45.061
Ooh! Ooh...

35:45.937 --> 35:48.147
What was that thing
about the spell?

35:48.898 --> 35:51.818
Did you say something about

35:52.777 --> 35:54.904
the spell?

35:57.907 --> 36:02.912
<i>Mor'du, Mor'du, now the time has
come for all of us to slaughter you.</i>

36:03.663 --> 36:04.722
<font color="#0080FF">ALL</font>: Hooray!

36:04.747 --> 36:06.165
<i>Mor'du, Mor'du...</i>

36:07.750 --> 36:09.752
<font color="#808080">(DISTANT SINGING)</font>

36:24.934 --> 36:26.994
<font color="#0080FF">ELINOR</font>: - Merida.
- Mum!

36:27.019 --> 36:28.913
Ooh, uh... I, uh...

36:28.938 --> 36:32.083
- Oh, I've been worried sick.
- You... You were?

36:32.108 --> 36:35.711
I didn't know where you'd
gone or when you'd come back.

36:35.736 --> 36:38.673
I didn't know what to think.
Oh, look at your dress.

36:38.698 --> 36:41.634
Oh. Angus threw me.
But I'm not hurt.

36:41.659 --> 36:45.788
Well, you're home now,
so that's the end of it.

36:46.789 --> 36:50.184
- Honestly?
- I've pacified the lords for now.

36:50.209 --> 36:53.229
Your father's out there
"entertaining" them.

36:53.254 --> 36:55.106
<i>Come taste my blade,
you manky bear.</i>

36:55.131 --> 36:56.799
<i>For gobbling up my leg.</i>

36:57.216 --> 37:00.987
<i>I'll hunt you, then I'll skin
you, hang your noggin on a Peg...</i>

37:01.012 --> 37:02.221
<font color="#808080">(CHEERING)</font>

37:03.306 --> 37:07.143
Of course, we both know a
decision still has to be made.

37:11.105 --> 37:13.958
- What's this?
- It's a peace offering.

37:13.983 --> 37:17.211
I made it.
For you. Special.

37:17.236 --> 37:20.114
You made this for me?

37:21.824 --> 37:22.867
Mm.

37:25.786 --> 37:28.639
Oh.
Interesting flavor.

37:28.664 --> 37:31.684
- How do you feel?
- What... What is that?

37:31.709 --> 37:33.336
- Different?
- Mm...

37:33.586 --> 37:36.939
Tart and, um, <font color="#808080">(GULPS)</font>
gamy.

37:36.964 --> 37:40.676
Have you changed your mind at all
about the marriage and all that?

37:41.677 --> 37:43.237
Oh, that's better.

37:43.262 --> 37:45.823
Now, why don't we go
upstairs to the lords

37:45.848 --> 37:48.826
and put this whole
kerfuffle to rest?

37:48.851 --> 37:50.186
Hm?

37:54.649 --> 37:56.067
<font color="#808080">(CELTIC FLUTE MUSIC PLAYING)</font>

37:56.859 --> 37:57.960
Ooh.

37:57.985 --> 38:00.838
- Mother?
- I'm woozy suddenly.

38:00.863 --> 38:03.341
My head's spinning like a top.
Ooh!

38:03.366 --> 38:07.178
- Mum!
- Oh, suddenly I'm not so well.

38:07.203 --> 38:11.098
Er... How... How do you feel
about the marriage now?

38:11.123 --> 38:14.185
Merida! Oh, just
take me to my room.

38:14.210 --> 38:16.854
<font color="#0080FF">FERGUS</font>: Alright, that's fine.
That's just fine.

38:16.879 --> 38:20.775
A little to the left. That's good. A
wee bit to the left. That's good.

38:20.800 --> 38:22.318
It's good enough.

38:22.343 --> 38:24.903
Now, clear out of there, boys. I
don't want you to spoil my shot.

38:25.388 --> 38:27.198
- What? <font color="#808080">(CLEARS THROAT)</font>
- My lady Queen.

38:27.223 --> 38:30.201
We've been waiting patiently.

38:30.226 --> 38:35.289
Milords, I am out of
sorts at the moment.

38:35.314 --> 38:39.168
But you shall have your answer.
<font color="#808080">(BURPS)</font>

38:39.193 --> 38:40.711
- Oh!
- Eh?

38:40.736 --> 38:42.755
Presently.

38:42.780 --> 38:45.741
Now, if you'll...
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font> excuse us.

38:47.410 --> 38:49.053
<font color="#808080">(ALL CHEERING)</font>
<font color="#0080FF">FERGUS</font>: - Elinor, look!

38:49.078 --> 38:51.080
It's Mor'du!
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font>

38:52.748 --> 38:54.684
Elinor?
Are you alright, dear?

38:54.709 --> 38:56.602
Fine.
I'm fine.

38:56.627 --> 38:58.938
Go about avenging your leg.
Oh...

38:58.963 --> 39:01.065
Aye.
You heard her, lads.

39:01.090 --> 39:05.236
I dream about the perfect
way to make this devil die.

39:05.261 --> 39:06.595
<font color="#808080">(ALL CHEERING)</font>

39:08.639 --> 39:12.660
Just take all the time you need
to getting yourself right, Mum.

39:12.685 --> 39:16.706
Then maybe in a bit you might have
something new to say on the marriage.

39:16.731 --> 39:19.208
What was in that cake?

39:19.233 --> 39:20.818
<font color="#808080">(SCOFFS)</font>
Cake.

39:20.943 --> 39:22.611
<font color="#808080">(COUGHS)</font>
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

39:23.029 --> 39:24.255
Mum?

39:24.280 --> 39:27.008
So I'll just tell them
the wedding's off, then?

39:27.033 --> 39:29.035
<font color="#808080">(ELINOR GROANING)</font>

39:32.038 --> 39:34.040
Mum?

39:37.626 --> 39:39.628
<font color="#808080">(DEEP GROANING)</font>

39:50.056 --> 39:51.807
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>

39:54.685 --> 39:56.979
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

39:58.105 --> 39:59.356
<font color="#808080">(LOW GROWLING)</font>

40:01.067 --> 40:02.151
Bear!

40:03.194 --> 40:04.920
<font color="#808080">(WHINES)</font>

40:04.945 --> 40:07.006
<font color="#808080">(FRIGHTENED GROWL)</font>

40:07.031 --> 40:08.282
<font color="#808080">(PANTING)</font>

40:10.868 --> 40:12.953
<font color="#808080">(GROWLS)</font>
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

40:21.378 --> 40:24.090
<font color="#808080">(SURPRISED ROARING)</font>

40:25.966 --> 40:26.967
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>
- Oh!

40:36.435 --> 40:37.978
Mum?

40:39.730 --> 40:42.983
You're... You're a bear!

40:44.026 --> 40:45.086
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

40:45.111 --> 40:46.487
Why a bear?

40:46.737 --> 40:50.741
Oh, that scaffy witch
gave me a gammy spell.

40:52.785 --> 40:54.178
It's not my fault.

40:54.203 --> 40:56.222
I didn't ask her to
change you into a bear.

40:56.247 --> 41:00.876
I just wanted her to change you.

41:02.253 --> 41:03.963
<font color="#808080">(ROARS)</font>

41:04.964 --> 41:06.899
<font color="#808080">(ALL CHEERING)</font>

41:06.924 --> 41:09.443
- Shh. Did you hear that?
- <font color="#808080">(SNIFFS)</font> <font color="#808080">(MUSIC STOPS)</font>

41:09.468 --> 41:11.779
Something's not right.

41:11.804 --> 41:14.140
<font color="#808080">(ANXIOUS WHINING)</font>

41:15.057 --> 41:18.410
There's no point in having a go
at me. The witch is to blame.

41:18.435 --> 41:20.813
Goggly old hag.

41:21.522 --> 41:23.983
Eyes all over the place.

41:24.775 --> 41:27.069
- Unbelievable.
- <font color="#808080">(GROANING)</font>

41:28.237 --> 41:30.881
- I'll get her to fix this.
- <font color="#808080">(SIGHS)</font>

41:30.906 --> 41:33.667
<font color="#0080FF">MERIDA</font>: Why do I always get blamed
for everything? It's just not fair.

41:34.910 --> 41:36.971
<font color="#808080">(SNIFFING)</font>

41:36.996 --> 41:39.306
Everybody, follow me.

41:39.331 --> 41:41.333
And keep a sharp eye.

41:42.960 --> 41:45.729
Here we go. Another hunt
through the castle.

41:45.754 --> 41:47.423
But we haven't had dessert yet.

41:47.548 --> 41:50.926
<font color="#808080">(SPEAKS IN THICK ACCENT)</font>

41:52.761 --> 41:54.763
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font>
I have no idea.

41:55.764 --> 41:58.392
<font color="#0080FF">MERIDA</font>: Mum, you
can't go out there.

41:59.435 --> 42:01.812
Mum! Wait!

42:03.439 --> 42:07.376
What are you doing? Dad.
The Bear King?

42:07.401 --> 42:09.570
If he so much as sees
you, you're dead.

42:09.820 --> 42:13.465
<font color="#0080FF">LORD DINGWALL</font>: Another one of your
entertainments to bore us to death!

42:13.490 --> 42:15.092
<font color="#0080FF">LORD MACINTOSH</font>: Oh, and what
exactly are we after...

42:15.117 --> 42:16.177
Mum!

42:16.202 --> 42:18.095
<font color="#0080FF">LORD MACINTOSH</font>: My liege?

42:18.120 --> 42:21.348
<font color="#0080FF">LORD MACGUFFIN</font>: Best to humor
him. He is, after all, the King.

42:21.373 --> 42:22.416
<font color="#808080">(SNIFFING)</font>

42:25.211 --> 42:27.588
He's like a hound with
that nose of his.

42:27.838 --> 42:29.023
<font color="#808080">(LICKS AND SPITS)</font>

42:29.048 --> 42:30.941
Mum, wait.

42:30.966 --> 42:32.443
- We have to...
- <font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

42:32.468 --> 42:34.904
<font color="#808080">(CLATTERING)</font>
- Follow me.

42:34.929 --> 42:36.555
Stop.

42:36.805 --> 42:37.848
Stop!

42:39.183 --> 42:40.184
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>

42:41.185 --> 42:43.412
You're covered with fur.

42:43.437 --> 42:45.164
You're not naked.

42:45.189 --> 42:47.149
It's not like anyone's
gonna see you.

42:52.154 --> 42:53.572
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

42:54.490 --> 42:56.091
Now you've done it.

42:56.116 --> 42:57.868
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

42:58.452 --> 43:00.304
Maudie!

43:00.329 --> 43:03.098
<font color="#808080">(STUTTERING)</font>
- Just calm down, lass. What is it?

43:03.123 --> 43:05.309
<font color="#808080">(STUTTERING)</font>
- Spit it out, Maudie!

43:05.334 --> 43:07.228
<font color="#808080">(SHOUTING)</font>
A bear!

43:07.253 --> 43:08.938
I knew it! <font color="#808080">(YELLS)</font>

43:08.963 --> 43:10.147
<font color="#808080">(ALL SHOUTING)</font>

43:10.172 --> 43:12.024
Would you just listen to me?

43:12.049 --> 43:14.985
- We can't go this way. You'll be seen.
- <font color="#808080">(MEN YELLING)</font>

43:15.010 --> 43:16.303
Quick! This way!

43:18.681 --> 43:19.682
Mum?

43:25.938 --> 43:27.690
<font color="#808080">(WHIMPERS)</font>

43:33.112 --> 43:34.238
<font color="#808080">(ALL GASP)</font>

43:35.906 --> 43:37.616
<font color="#808080">(SOFTLY)</font>
Mum? Oh!

43:37.866 --> 43:39.868
<font color="#808080">(MEN SHOUTING)</font>

43:43.163 --> 43:45.291
- Oh!
- <font color="#808080">(ELINOR WHINING)</font>

43:54.300 --> 43:55.342
Hm?

43:56.427 --> 43:59.655
A witch turned Mum into a bear.
It's not my fault.

43:59.680 --> 44:02.057
We've got to get out of the
castle. I need your help.

44:02.599 --> 44:04.368
Oh, alright.

44:04.393 --> 44:07.688
You can have my desserts
for two... Three weeks.

44:09.398 --> 44:11.525
Okay. Fine. A year.

44:17.573 --> 44:19.383
- Did you hear that?
- Shh.

44:19.408 --> 44:21.285
<font color="#808080">(ECHOING ROAR)</font>

44:23.620 --> 44:25.914
<font color="#808080">(ECHOING ROAR)</font>

44:27.124 --> 44:29.376
- There it goes!
- <font color="#808080">(MEN SHOUTING)</font>

44:30.643 --> 44:32.563
<font color="#808080">(MOCK ROARING CONTINUES)</font> <font color="#0080FF">FERGUS</font>:
- Come on, lads!

44:32.588 --> 44:34.423
<font color="#808080">(YELLS)</font>

44:36.592 --> 44:39.011
<font color="#808080">(YELLS)</font>
<font color="#808080">(MOCK GROWLING)</font>

44:40.429 --> 44:41.513
There it goes!

44:43.057 --> 44:44.767
<font color="#808080">(ALL YELLING)</font>

44:50.105 --> 44:51.648
<font color="#808080">(BIRD CALL)</font>

44:55.110 --> 44:57.463
- Come on, Mum.
- <font color="#808080">(WHINES)</font>

44:57.488 --> 44:59.406
<font color="#808080">(CLATTERING)</font>

45:00.746 --> 45:02.426
<font color="#0080FF">LORD MACGUFFIN</font>: Think
we should lay a trap?

45:02.451 --> 45:04.219
<font color="#0080FF">FERGUS</font>: Try shutting yours!

45:04.244 --> 45:06.263
<font color="#808080">(ALL ARGUING)</font>

45:06.288 --> 45:07.681
<font color="#808080">(MOCK GROWLING)</font>

45:07.706 --> 45:09.541
- There he is!
- <font color="#808080">(MEN SHOUTING)</font>

45:14.505 --> 45:16.256
<font color="#808080">(ALL SHOUTING)</font>

45:21.970 --> 45:23.697
<font color="#0080FF">FERGUS</font>: I'm sure
it went this way.

45:23.722 --> 45:25.324
<font color="#0080FF">LORD MACGUFFIN</font>: You can
see my house from here.

45:25.349 --> 45:27.326
It must have sprouted wings.

45:27.351 --> 45:30.579
Was carried away
by a giant birdy.

45:30.604 --> 45:33.624
- A dragon, perhaps.
- Bear in the castle!

45:33.649 --> 45:36.085
Doesn't make sense.
It cannot open doors.

45:36.110 --> 45:38.045
He's got big giant paws!

45:38.070 --> 45:39.446
Let's just get inside.

45:40.155 --> 45:41.590
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTING)</font>

45:41.615 --> 45:44.385
- It's locked.
- Dingwall was the last up.

45:44.410 --> 45:46.637
<font color="#0080FF">LORD DINGWALL</font>: I propped
it open with a stick.

45:46.662 --> 45:48.330
<font color="#808080">(MEN GRUMBLING)</font>

45:52.709 --> 45:56.397
<font color="#0080FF">HANDMAID</font>: What did you see,
Maudie? Just spit it out, Maudie.

45:56.422 --> 45:58.982
Oh, for goodness' sakes,
Maudie, would you get a grip?

45:59.007 --> 46:00.008
<font color="#808080">(CLATTERING)</font>

46:02.344 --> 46:04.446
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

46:04.471 --> 46:06.471
<font color="#0080FF">HANDMAID</font>: Maudie, honey,
come here! It's alright!

46:07.641 --> 46:09.184
Come on, Mum.
Quick.

46:10.102 --> 46:11.161
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

46:11.186 --> 46:12.604
Shh.

46:18.527 --> 46:20.612
<font color="#808080">(CRASHING AND CLATTERING)</font>

46:22.197 --> 46:24.199
<font color="#808080">(CLATTERING)</font>

46:25.451 --> 46:27.119
<font color="#808080">(GIGGLING)</font>

46:27.411 --> 46:28.412
<font color="#808080">(SNEEZES)</font>

46:29.246 --> 46:30.472
<font color="#808080">(WHINES)</font>

46:30.497 --> 46:32.349
They'll be fine.
Won't you, boys?

46:32.374 --> 46:33.375
<font color="#808080">(SNIFFS)</font>

46:33.792 --> 46:36.186
Mum, we've got to hurry.

46:36.211 --> 46:37.688
Now, I'll be back soon.

46:37.713 --> 46:41.008
Go on and help yourself to
anything you want, as a reward.

46:42.801 --> 46:44.636
<font color="#808080">(ALL GASP)</font>

46:55.230 --> 46:57.666
<font color="#808080">(STRAINING)</font>
Oh!

46:57.691 --> 46:58.692
<font color="#808080">(LORD DINGWALL SIGHS)</font>

46:58.817 --> 47:00.527
Right!

47:07.659 --> 47:09.761
<font color="#0080FF">MERIDA</font>: Where are these wisps?

47:09.786 --> 47:13.123
Come out, wisps. Come on out.

47:14.750 --> 47:17.336
Lead me to the witch's cottage.

47:18.462 --> 47:20.464
I'm here!

47:21.381 --> 47:25.027
Fine. Don't come out now
that my mum's watching.

47:25.052 --> 47:26.153
<font color="#808080">(WHINES)</font>

47:26.178 --> 47:31.241
I was standing right here and
the wisp appeared right there.

47:31.266 --> 47:34.686
Then a whole trail of them
led me off into the Forest.

47:40.776 --> 47:45.113
Oh, does she think we're just going
to happen upon the witch's cottage?

47:46.156 --> 47:47.574
<font color="#808080">(OWLS HOOTING)</font>

47:53.664 --> 47:55.290
<font color="#808080">(DISTANT HOWLING)</font>

47:59.127 --> 48:01.338
Oh, Mum, I know this place.

48:01.880 --> 48:03.840
The witch's cottage...

48:04.633 --> 48:07.803
It's this way!
Come on! Hurry!

48:17.187 --> 48:20.207
I can't believe it.
I found it.

48:20.232 --> 48:22.067
<font color="#808080">(WHINES)</font>

48:24.695 --> 48:27.447
No. She was here.

48:28.407 --> 48:31.635
No, really, she was just here.

48:31.660 --> 48:32.869
<font color="#808080">(WHINES)</font>

48:33.161 --> 48:34.621
Oh, wait.

48:39.293 --> 48:41.395
- No.
- <font color="#808080">(BANGS DOOR SHUT)</font>

48:41.420 --> 48:44.840
No, no. No! No!

48:47.092 --> 48:49.236
<font color="#808080">(METAL RATTLES)</font>
- Oh.

48:49.261 --> 48:51.513
<font color="#808080">(RUMBLING)</font>

48:53.682 --> 48:54.766
<font color="#808080">(DINGING)</font>

48:57.269 --> 48:59.438
<font color="#808080">(SHRIEKS)</font>

49:00.355 --> 49:02.357
<font color="#808080">(BUBBLING)</font>

49:09.781 --> 49:12.676
<i>Welcome to the Crafty Carver,</i>

49:12.701 --> 49:16.221
<i>home of bear-themed
carvings and novelties.</i>

49:16.246 --> 49:19.433
<i>I am completely out of
stock at this time.</i>

49:19.458 --> 49:24.813
<i>But if you'd like to enquire about
portraits or wedding cake toppers,</i>

49:24.838 --> 49:26.857
<i>pour vial one into
the cauldron.</i>

49:26.882 --> 49:29.610
<i>If you'd like the menu
in Gaelic, vial two.</i>

49:29.635 --> 49:32.529
<i>If you're that red-haired
lass, vial three.</i>

49:32.554 --> 49:34.890
<i>To speak with a
live homunculus...</i>

49:35.557 --> 49:39.494
<i>Princess, I'm off to the
Wickerman Festival in Stornoway</i>

49:39.519 --> 49:41.538
<i>and won't be back till spring.</i>

49:41.563 --> 49:45.250
<i>There's one bit I forgot to
tell you about the spell.</i>

49:45.275 --> 49:49.212
<i>By the second sunrise, your
spell will be permanent,</i>

49:49.237 --> 49:53.575
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font> <i>unless you
remember these words.</i>

49:54.576 --> 49:56.720
<i>Fate be changed,</i>

49:56.745 --> 49:58.722
<i>look inside,</i>

49:58.747 --> 50:00.724
<i>mend the bond</i>

50:00.749 --> 50:02.851
<i>torn by pride.</i>

50:02.876 --> 50:06.980
"Fate be changed... Mend the
bond." What does that mean?

50:07.005 --> 50:08.732
<i>One more time.</i>

50:08.757 --> 50:10.692
<i>Fate be changed,</i>

50:10.717 --> 50:12.819
<i>look inside,</i>

50:12.844 --> 50:14.696
<i>mend the bond</i>

50:14.721 --> 50:17.324
<i>torn by pride.</i>

50:17.349 --> 50:18.742
<i>That's it. Ta-Ta.</i>

50:18.767 --> 50:22.704
<i>Oh, and thank you for shopping
at the Crafty Carver.</i>

50:22.729 --> 50:25.415
No. No!
Where'd you go?

50:25.440 --> 50:28.001
- <i>Welcome to the Crafty Carver...</i>
- What?

50:28.026 --> 50:30.295
<i>For all your...</i>
<font color="#808080">(SPEECH OVERLAPPING)</font>

50:30.320 --> 50:34.616
Maybe there's a book of spells.
Look around. We'll need more vials.

50:36.493 --> 50:39.596
<i>I'm off to the Wickerman
Festival in Stornoway...</i>

50:39.621 --> 50:41.790
<font color="#808080">(SCRAMBLED MESSAGES)</font>

50:42.499 --> 50:45.602
<i>Thank you for visiting.
Have a lovely day.</i>

50:45.627 --> 50:46.628
<font color="#808080">(BANG)</font>

50:51.425 --> 50:53.427
<font color="#808080">(WHINES SOFTLY)</font>

51:04.271 --> 51:06.248
<font color="#808080">(RAIN PATTERING)</font>

51:06.273 --> 51:07.482
<font color="#808080">(MERIDA STRAINING)</font>

51:18.326 --> 51:19.453
<font color="#808080">(ELINOR SIGHS)</font>

51:22.539 --> 51:24.791
We'll sort it out tomorrow.

51:43.059 --> 51:45.187
<font color="#808080">(THUNDER RUMBLING)</font>

51:53.111 --> 51:55.113
<font color="#808080">(FAINT SINGING)</font>

51:58.575 --> 52:00.577
<font color="#808080">(ELINOR SINGING IN GAELIC)</font>

52:07.501 --> 52:09.711
<font color="#808080">(CRACK OF THUNDER)</font>
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

52:10.378 --> 52:12.422
Oh.
<font color="#808080">(SPEAKS GAELIC)</font>

52:13.381 --> 52:16.526
My brave wee Lassie, I'm here.

52:16.551 --> 52:19.554
I'll always be right here.

52:21.473 --> 52:23.475
<font color="#808080">(CONTINUES SINGING IN GAELIC)</font>

52:25.101 --> 52:27.103
<font color="#808080">(BOTH SINGING)</font>

52:38.740 --> 52:40.742
<font color="#808080">(BIRDSONG)</font>

52:41.785 --> 52:44.012
Uh... Good morning.

52:44.037 --> 52:46.056
<font color="#808080">(MOANS)</font>

52:46.081 --> 52:48.124
So...
<font color="#808080">(CHUCKLES)</font>

52:48.416 --> 52:51.645
- What's all this supposed to be?
- <font color="#808080">(SIGHS)</font>

52:51.670 --> 52:53.480
Oh.

52:53.505 --> 52:55.732
<font color="#808080">(MOANS AND GRUNTS)</font>

52:55.757 --> 52:57.484
What?

52:57.509 --> 52:59.845
<font color="#808080">(HUFFS AND SNORTS)</font>

53:04.182 --> 53:06.159
Sorry.
I don't speak bear.

53:06.184 --> 53:07.227
<font color="#808080">(HUFFS)</font>

53:11.189 --> 53:12.691
Oh.

53:13.733 --> 53:14.734
<font color="#808080">(MOANS)</font>

53:17.487 --> 53:18.588
Ah!

53:18.613 --> 53:19.781
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTS IN SURPRISE)</font>

53:23.702 --> 53:24.703
<font color="#808080">(SLURPS)</font>

53:27.122 --> 53:29.850
- Find those by the creek, did you?
- Mm-hm.

53:29.875 --> 53:31.309
They're nightshade berries.

53:31.334 --> 53:33.086
Mmm.

53:33.795 --> 53:35.422
They're poisonous.

53:37.132 --> 53:38.133
<font color="#808080">(SPUTTERING)</font>

53:43.972 --> 53:47.017
Where did you get this water?
It has worms.

53:50.103 --> 53:51.980
<font color="#808080">(GULPS)</font>

53:52.981 --> 53:54.082
<font color="#808080">(THUDDING)</font>

53:54.107 --> 53:55.859
<font color="#808080">(BIRDS SQUAWK)</font>

53:57.861 --> 54:00.780
<font color="#808080">(GIGGLES)</font> Come on.
<font color="#808080">(GROWLS SOFTLY)</font>

54:08.830 --> 54:09.998
Breakfast.

54:10.665 --> 54:11.808
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTS APPROVINGLY)</font>

54:11.833 --> 54:16.755
Oh, wait. A Princess should not
have weapons, in your opinion.

54:16.880 --> 54:18.648
Uh-huh... <font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

54:18.673 --> 54:20.091
There you go.

54:21.593 --> 54:23.069
Go on.

54:23.094 --> 54:24.971
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

54:25.847 --> 54:28.533
How do you know you don't
like it if you won't try it?

54:28.558 --> 54:29.851
<font color="#808080">(WHINES)</font>

54:38.485 --> 54:39.569
<font color="#808080">(GROANS APPROVINGLY)</font>

54:43.949 --> 54:45.450
Mm.

54:46.201 --> 54:47.202
<font color="#808080">(MUNCHING LOUDLY)</font>

54:53.458 --> 54:54.918
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTS)</font>

54:55.710 --> 54:57.145
<font color="#808080">(BURPS)</font>

54:57.170 --> 54:58.355
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

54:58.380 --> 55:00.190
<font color="#808080">(SLOW SONG PLAYING)</font>

55:00.215 --> 55:04.694
<i>This love it is
a distant star.</i>

55:04.719 --> 55:08.848
<i>Guiding us home
wherever we are.</i>

55:09.808 --> 55:13.937
<i>This love it is a burning sun.</i>

55:14.187 --> 55:18.483
<i>Shining light on the
things that we've done.</i>

55:19.401 --> 55:25.298
<i>I tried to speak
to you every day.</i>

55:25.323 --> 55:32.247
<i>But each word we spoke
the wind blew away.</i>

55:36.292 --> 55:39.587
<i>How did we let
it come to this?</i>

55:41.006 --> 55:42.816
<i>What we just tasted...</i>

55:42.841 --> 55:44.759
<font color="#808080">(MERIDA LAUGHS)</font>

55:47.178 --> 55:52.684
<i>How will it feel when
this day is done?</i>

55:53.018 --> 55:59.983
<i>And can we keep what
we've only begun?</i>

56:00.650 --> 56:01.751
<font color="#808080">(CRIES OUT)</font>

56:01.776 --> 56:07.449
<i>Could these walls
come crumbling down?</i>

56:08.616 --> 56:14.622
<i>I want to feel my
feet on the ground.</i>

56:15.582 --> 56:20.378
<i>Can we carry this
love that we share.</i>

56:21.504 --> 56:26.217
<i>Into the open air.</i>

56:28.511 --> 56:34.142
<i>Into the open air.</i>

56:36.478 --> 56:37.604
Hey!

56:39.272 --> 56:41.649
Where are you going?

56:47.280 --> 56:52.410
<i>This love it is a burning sun.</i>

56:52.660 --> 56:55.013
Mum, come back.

56:55.038 --> 56:56.664
<font color="#808080">(GROWLS)</font>

57:01.002 --> 57:02.896
- Uh...
- <font color="#808080">(SNARLS)</font>

57:02.921 --> 57:03.963
- Oh...
- <font color="#808080">(GROWLING)</font>

57:07.926 --> 57:10.053
Mum, is that you?

57:11.137 --> 57:13.198
<font color="#808080">(ROARS)</font>

57:13.223 --> 57:15.934
Uh... Mum?

57:17.644 --> 57:19.687
<font color="#808080">(WHINES)</font>

57:22.690 --> 57:24.751
You changed.

57:24.776 --> 57:26.194
Like you were a...

57:27.112 --> 57:30.573
I mean, like you were
a bear on the inside.

57:31.032 --> 57:33.076
<font color="#808080">(WHINES AND SNORTS)</font>

57:39.374 --> 57:40.433
<font color="#808080">(WISP CALLS)</font>

57:40.458 --> 57:42.018
A wisp.

57:42.043 --> 57:44.729
- Mum!
- <font color="#808080">(WISP SQUEAKS)</font>

57:44.754 --> 57:46.756
Stop it!

57:47.715 --> 57:49.384
Mum, no!

57:50.593 --> 57:51.694
<font color="#808080">(WISP CALLING)</font>

57:51.719 --> 57:53.721
Mum...

57:55.014 --> 57:56.015
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTS)</font>

57:58.560 --> 58:01.246
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>
- Jings, crivens, help ma boab.

58:01.271 --> 58:03.832
Mum, I know you're scared,

58:03.857 --> 58:06.876
you're tired, you
don't understand,

58:06.901 --> 58:10.213
but we've got to keep our heads.

58:10.238 --> 58:12.657
Just calm down.

58:13.158 --> 58:15.160
Listen.

58:18.872 --> 58:19.873
<font color="#808080">(FAINT WHISPERING)</font>

58:24.210 --> 58:26.212
<font color="#808080">(FAINT WHISPERING CONTINUES)</font>

58:34.888 --> 58:36.890
<font color="#808080">(WISP CALLS)</font>

58:43.646 --> 58:45.106
They'll show us the way.

58:48.067 --> 58:50.069
<font color="#808080">(WISPS CALLING)</font>

59:00.330 --> 59:02.957
<font color="#808080">(WISP CALLING)</font>

59:13.384 --> 59:15.178
<font color="#0080FF">MERIDA</font>: Mum, look.

59:22.018 --> 59:23.244
<font color="#808080">(WIND WHISTLES)</font>

59:23.269 --> 59:25.205
<font color="#808080">(ELINOR BEAR GROANS)</font>

59:25.230 --> 59:27.815
<font color="#0080FF">MERIDA</font>: Why did the
wisps bring us here?

59:27.941 --> 59:29.442
<font color="#808080">(ELINOR BEAR MOANS)</font>

59:34.614 --> 59:36.658
<font color="#808080">(ELINOR BEAR HUFFS AND SNORTS)</font>

59:54.926 --> 59:57.403
Whoever they were, they've been
gone for a long, long time.

59:57.428 --> 59:59.931
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

01:00:01.474 --> 01:00:03.076
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

01:00:03.101 --> 01:00:05.912
<font color="#808080">(WHINES)</font>
- I'm fine, Mum.

01:00:05.937 --> 01:00:07.313
Just fine.

01:00:16.990 --> 01:00:18.992
It's, uh,

01:00:19.867 --> 01:00:20.952
a throne room.

01:00:22.745 --> 01:00:24.514
You suppose this could've
been the kingdom

01:00:24.539 --> 01:00:26.307
in that story you
were telling me?

01:00:26.332 --> 01:00:29.168
<font color="#808080">(MOANS)</font>
- The one with the princes.

01:00:29.711 --> 01:00:31.045
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

01:00:32.964 --> 01:00:34.549
One,

01:00:34.841 --> 01:00:35.984
two,

01:00:36.009 --> 01:00:37.527
three,

01:00:37.552 --> 01:00:39.445
four.

01:00:39.470 --> 01:00:41.347
The oldest.

01:00:41.639 --> 01:00:42.640
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

01:00:44.309 --> 01:00:46.477
Split, like the tapestry.

01:00:48.062 --> 01:00:49.122
<font color="#808080">(GROWLING)</font>

01:00:49.147 --> 01:00:50.523
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>

01:00:52.108 --> 01:00:55.445
The spell.
It's happened before.

01:01:00.033 --> 01:01:02.535
"Strength of ten men."

01:01:03.870 --> 01:01:06.080
"Fate be changed."

01:01:08.249 --> 01:01:11.127
"Changed his fate."

01:01:12.211 --> 01:01:13.896
Oh, no.

01:01:13.921 --> 01:01:15.965
The Prince became...

01:01:18.801 --> 01:01:20.261
<font color="#808080">(GROWLING)</font>

01:01:21.846 --> 01:01:23.906
- Mor'du.
- <font color="#808080">(ROARS)</font>

01:01:23.931 --> 01:01:25.266
<font color="#808080">(ROARING)</font>

01:01:27.477 --> 01:01:29.103
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

01:01:33.733 --> 01:01:35.335
<font color="#808080">(GROANING)</font>

01:01:35.360 --> 01:01:36.986
<font color="#808080">(ROARS)</font>
<font color="#808080">(FABRIC TEARING)</font>

01:01:41.574 --> 01:01:43.368
<font color="#808080">(WHIMPERING)</font>
<font color="#808080">(ROARS)</font>

01:01:51.501 --> 01:01:52.502
<font color="#808080">(SNARLS)</font>

01:01:58.591 --> 01:01:59.634
<font color="#808080">(MOANS)</font>

01:02:08.851 --> 01:02:10.103
<font color="#808080">(HUFFING AND PANTING)</font>

01:02:15.983 --> 01:02:17.944
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

01:02:19.445 --> 01:02:21.489
<font color="#808080">(CREAKING)</font>

01:02:25.076 --> 01:02:27.203
<font color="#808080">(MERIDA GROANS)</font>

01:02:29.288 --> 01:02:31.999
Mum, we need to get
back to the castle.

01:02:32.625 --> 01:02:35.978
If we don't hurry, you'll
become like Mor'du.

01:02:36.003 --> 01:02:37.438
A bear!

01:02:37.463 --> 01:02:39.632
A real bear.
Forever!

01:02:39.882 --> 01:02:43.469
<font color="#808080">(WHINES)</font>
- "Mend the bond torn by pride."

01:02:44.262 --> 01:02:47.890
The witch gave us the answer.
The tapestry.

01:02:56.649 --> 01:03:00.361
<font color="#808080">(ELINOR GRUMBLES)</font>
- Mum, do you have a better idea?

01:03:01.654 --> 01:03:03.030
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTS)</font>

01:03:15.293 --> 01:03:16.586
<font color="#808080">(STRAINING)</font>

01:03:18.629 --> 01:03:20.006
That'll do.

01:03:21.507 --> 01:03:23.509
<font color="#808080">(TALKING INDISTINCTLY)</font>

01:03:27.555 --> 01:03:29.474
<font color="#808080">(MEN SHOUTING)</font>

01:03:34.687 --> 01:03:37.415
No more talk. No
more traditions.

01:03:37.440 --> 01:03:38.875
We settle this now!

01:03:38.900 --> 01:03:40.543
You're the King.

01:03:40.568 --> 01:03:44.547
You decide which one of our
sons your daughter will marry.

01:03:44.572 --> 01:03:47.717
None of your sons are fit
to marry my daughter.

01:03:47.742 --> 01:03:50.745
Then our alliance is over!
This means war!

01:03:51.913 --> 01:03:53.581
<font color="#808080">(SHOUTING)</font>

01:03:55.541 --> 01:03:57.268
They're gonna murder each other.

01:03:57.293 --> 01:03:59.812
You've got to stop them
before it's too late.

01:03:59.837 --> 01:04:01.522
<font color="#808080">(WHINES)</font>

01:04:01.547 --> 01:04:03.024
I know, I know!

01:04:03.049 --> 01:04:05.776
But how do we get you through
there and up to the tapestry

01:04:05.801 --> 01:04:07.845
with the lot of them
boiling over like that?

01:04:08.596 --> 01:04:10.389
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTS)</font>
- Oh!

01:04:14.310 --> 01:04:16.479
<font color="#808080">(SHOUTING)</font>

01:04:22.318 --> 01:04:23.778
<font color="#808080">(SHOUTING STOPS)</font>

01:04:26.948 --> 01:04:30.593
- What are you doing, lass?
- It's alright, Dad.

01:04:30.618 --> 01:04:33.287
<font color="#808080">(CLEARS THROAT)</font>
I, um...

01:04:34.038 --> 01:04:36.374
I have...

01:04:36.999 --> 01:04:39.977
Well, you see, I...

01:04:40.002 --> 01:04:42.647
I have been in conference
with the Queen.

01:04:42.672 --> 01:04:45.608
- Is that so?
- Aye, it is.

01:04:45.633 --> 01:04:47.944
- Well, where is she, then?
- She, uh...

01:04:47.969 --> 01:04:50.112
How do we know that
this isn't some trick?

01:04:50.137 --> 01:04:52.031
- I'd never...
- This is highly irregular.

01:04:52.056 --> 01:04:53.991
- What are you playing at?
- Where is the Queen?

01:04:54.016 --> 01:04:56.661
<font color="#0080FF">LORD MACINTOSH</font>: We will not stand for
any more of this jiggery-pokery.

01:04:56.686 --> 01:04:58.913
- That's right. Let's see her.
- Shut it!

01:04:58.938 --> 01:04:59.939
<font color="#808080">(SILENCE)</font>

01:05:01.107 --> 01:05:02.233
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font>

01:05:02.525 --> 01:05:03.626
<font color="#808080">(CLEARS THROAT)</font>

01:05:03.651 --> 01:05:05.820
Well, I, uh...

01:05:09.991 --> 01:05:10.992
Uh...

01:05:15.454 --> 01:05:19.083
Once there was an
ancient kingdom.

01:05:19.333 --> 01:05:21.018
What is this?

01:05:21.043 --> 01:05:24.647
That kingdom fell into war

01:05:24.672 --> 01:05:26.816
and chaos and ruin...

01:05:26.841 --> 01:05:29.986
Och, we've all heard that tale.
Lost kingdom.

01:05:30.011 --> 01:05:31.654
Aye, but it's true.

01:05:31.679 --> 01:05:35.366
I know now how one selfish act
can turn the fate of a kingdom.

01:05:35.391 --> 01:05:36.826
<font color="#0080FF">LORD MACGUFFIN</font>: Bah,
it's just a legend.

01:05:36.851 --> 01:05:38.603
Legends are lessons.

01:05:39.395 --> 01:05:41.480
They ring with truths.

01:05:42.523 --> 01:05:44.108
Our kingdom is young.

01:05:44.358 --> 01:05:46.502
Our stories are not yet legend.

01:05:46.527 --> 01:05:49.714
But in them, our
bond was struck.

01:05:49.739 --> 01:05:51.924
Our clans were once enemies.

01:05:51.949 --> 01:05:55.344
But when invaders
threatened us from the sea,

01:05:55.369 --> 01:05:58.372
you joined together
to defend our lands.

01:05:58.914 --> 01:06:01.642
You fought for each other.

01:06:01.667 --> 01:06:03.628
You risked everything
for each other.

01:06:04.545 --> 01:06:07.023
Lord MacGuffin, my
Dad saved your life,

01:06:07.048 --> 01:06:09.650
stopping an arrow as you
ran to Dingwall's aid.

01:06:09.675 --> 01:06:11.527
Aye, and I'll never forget it.

01:06:11.552 --> 01:06:13.279
<font color="#0080FF">MERIDA</font>: And, Lord Macintosh,

01:06:13.304 --> 01:06:16.699
you saved my Dad when you
charged in on heavy horse

01:06:16.724 --> 01:06:18.492
and held off the advance.

01:06:18.517 --> 01:06:22.622
And we all know how Lord
Dingwall broke the enemy line.

01:06:22.647 --> 01:06:24.749
With a mighty throw
of his spear!

01:06:24.774 --> 01:06:26.709
I was aiming at you,
you big tumshie.

01:06:26.734 --> 01:06:28.152
<font color="#808080">(ALL LAUGH)</font>

01:06:28.527 --> 01:06:31.922
The story of this kingdom
is a powerful one.

01:06:31.947 --> 01:06:34.550
My Dad rallied your forces

01:06:34.575 --> 01:06:37.011
and you made him your King.

01:06:37.036 --> 01:06:41.182
It was an alliance forged
in bravery and friendship

01:06:41.207 --> 01:06:43.017
and it lives to this day.

01:06:43.042 --> 01:06:45.086
<font color="#808080">(ALL CHEERING)</font>

01:06:48.547 --> 01:06:51.067
But I've been selfish.

01:06:51.092 --> 01:06:54.136
I tore a great rift
in our kingdom.

01:06:54.970 --> 01:06:57.056
There's no one to blame but me.

01:06:57.890 --> 01:07:01.602
And I know now that I
need to amend my mistake

01:07:02.770 --> 01:07:04.438
and mend our bond.

01:07:05.981 --> 01:07:09.819
And so, there is the
matter of my betrothal.

01:07:11.237 --> 01:07:14.590
I've decided to do what's right

01:07:14.615 --> 01:07:15.783
and...

01:07:16.617 --> 01:07:18.244
and...

01:07:18.953 --> 01:07:20.663
and...

01:07:21.664 --> 01:07:24.850
break tradition.

01:07:24.875 --> 01:07:26.335
<font color="#808080">(GASPING AND MUTTERING)</font>

01:07:31.173 --> 01:07:33.008
My mother...

01:07:34.301 --> 01:07:36.971
the Queen, feels...

01:07:37.638 --> 01:07:40.866
uh, in her heart

01:07:40.891 --> 01:07:42.810
that I...

01:07:44.520 --> 01:07:47.189
that we be free to...

01:07:48.566 --> 01:07:52.153
write our own story...

01:07:53.904 --> 01:07:58.159
follow our hearts

01:07:59.118 --> 01:08:02.747
and find love in our own time.

01:08:06.500 --> 01:08:09.645
- That's <font color="#808080">(SNIFFS)</font> beautiful.
- <font color="#808080">(ALL SNIFFLING)</font>

01:08:09.670 --> 01:08:13.048
The Queen and I put the
decision to you, my lords.

01:08:13.924 --> 01:08:17.862
Might our young people decide for
themselves who they will love?

01:08:17.886 --> 01:08:18.988
Huh?

01:08:19.013 --> 01:08:22.198
Well, since you've obviously
made up your minds about this,

01:08:22.224 --> 01:08:24.243
I have one thing to say.

01:08:24.268 --> 01:08:26.828
- This is...
- A grand idea!

01:08:26.854 --> 01:08:29.206
Give us our own say
in choosing our fate.

01:08:29.231 --> 01:08:32.568
- What?!
- Aye. Why shouldn't we choose?

01:08:32.693 --> 01:08:34.795
But she's the Princess.

01:08:34.819 --> 01:08:37.840
I did not pick her out.
It was your idea.

01:08:37.865 --> 01:08:41.176
And you...
You feel the same way?

01:08:41.202 --> 01:08:46.223
<font color="#808080">(SPEAKS UNINTELLIGIBLY)</font>

01:08:46.247 --> 01:08:48.725
- Good?
- <font color="#808080">(GRUNTS)</font>

01:08:48.751 --> 01:08:50.044
<font color="#808080">(GIGGLES)</font>

01:08:51.337 --> 01:08:52.938
Well, that settles it.

01:08:52.962 --> 01:08:57.734
Let these lads try and win her
heart before they win her hand.

01:08:57.760 --> 01:08:59.153
If they can.

01:08:59.178 --> 01:09:02.198
I say, the wee Dingwall
has a fighting chance.

01:09:02.223 --> 01:09:04.700
Fine, then. Seems
for once we agree.

01:09:04.725 --> 01:09:07.828
- It was my idea in the first place.
- <font color="#808080">(ALL LAUGHING)</font>

01:09:07.853 --> 01:09:09.145
<font color="#808080">(SIGHS)</font>

01:09:13.024 --> 01:09:15.569
<font color="#808080">(ALL MUTTERING CONTENTEDLY)</font>

01:09:17.779 --> 01:09:19.715
Just like your mum.

01:09:19.740 --> 01:09:21.033
You devil.

01:09:24.078 --> 01:09:26.078
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>

01:09:26.705 --> 01:09:29.809
Uh... Everyone to the cellar!

01:09:29.834 --> 01:09:34.313
Let's crack open the King's
private reserve to celebrate!

01:09:34.337 --> 01:09:36.064
<font color="#808080">(ALL CHEERING)</font>

01:09:36.090 --> 01:09:37.399
Oh.

01:09:37.424 --> 01:09:39.859
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font>
Whoa, whoa, whoa.

01:09:39.885 --> 01:09:42.112
Psst.
Bring the tiny glasses.

01:09:42.136 --> 01:09:44.139
<font color="#808080">(TALKING AND LAUGHING)</font>

01:09:47.935 --> 01:09:49.036
<font color="#808080">(SIGHS)</font>

01:09:49.060 --> 01:09:50.437
<font color="#808080">(MERIDA GIGGLES)</font>

01:09:50.729 --> 01:09:52.773
<font color="#808080">(SINGS HAPPILY)</font>

01:09:56.110 --> 01:09:57.444
Oh, the tapestry!

01:10:00.239 --> 01:10:02.741
Mend the bond...

01:10:03.951 --> 01:10:06.095
Mend the bond.

01:10:06.120 --> 01:10:08.931
Stitch it up.
This'll change you back.

01:10:08.956 --> 01:10:11.292
We just need needle and thread.

01:10:11.417 --> 01:10:12.459
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTS)</font>

01:10:16.630 --> 01:10:17.731
<font color="#808080">(GROWLS)</font>

01:10:17.756 --> 01:10:19.842
- Mum?
- <font color="#808080">(SNARLS)</font>

01:10:21.468 --> 01:10:23.404
Mum?
Not now.

01:10:23.429 --> 01:10:26.098
No.
Please, not now.

01:10:26.307 --> 01:10:27.366
<font color="#808080">(SNIFFING)</font>

01:10:27.391 --> 01:10:28.993
- Mum...
- <font color="#808080">(MEN LAUGHING)</font>

01:10:29.018 --> 01:10:30.269
<font color="#808080">(GROWLS)</font>
- Shh.

01:10:32.104 --> 01:10:34.106
<font color="#808080">(SINGING JOVIALLY)</font>

01:10:37.484 --> 01:10:43.424
Elinor, clear, you'll never guess who
just solved our little suitor problem.

01:10:43.449 --> 01:10:46.660
<font color="#808080">(THUNDER RUMBLING)</font>
<font color="#808080">(FERGUS BREATHING HEAVILY)</font>

01:10:55.252 --> 01:10:56.587
Elinor!

01:10:59.340 --> 01:11:03.193
It can't be true! Elinor,
answer me, lass!

01:11:03.218 --> 01:11:05.346
Elinor!

01:11:06.430 --> 01:11:08.824
- Merida.
- <font color="#808080">(SNARLING)</font>

01:11:08.849 --> 01:11:11.201
- What?
- Dad, no! It's not what you think.

01:11:11.226 --> 01:11:13.329
- Merida, get back!
- No!

01:11:13.354 --> 01:11:14.772
<font color="#808080">(GROWLING)</font>

01:11:15.689 --> 01:11:17.024
<font color="#808080">(YELLING)</font>

01:11:18.359 --> 01:11:20.444
No, Dad! Don't hurt her!

01:11:21.362 --> 01:11:23.339
- Get out of here!
- <font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

01:11:23.364 --> 01:11:26.008
Merida!
No!

01:11:26.033 --> 01:11:27.034
<font color="#808080">(ROARS)</font>

01:11:27.201 --> 01:11:29.036
<font color="#808080">(YELLS)</font>

01:11:30.079 --> 01:11:32.456
- No!

01:11:34.458 --> 01:11:35.751
<font color="#808080">(MOANS)</font>

01:11:38.629 --> 01:11:40.130
<font color="#808080">(GROANING)</font>

01:11:40.297 --> 01:11:42.883
- Mum.
- <font color="#808080">(WHINES)</font>

01:11:44.218 --> 01:11:45.819
<font color="#808080">(WHIMPERS)</font>

01:11:45.844 --> 01:11:50.783
It's alright. I'm alright. It's nothing.
It's just a little scratch. Mum!

01:11:50.808 --> 01:11:52.826
- My liege!
- <font color="#808080">(ALL LAUGHING)</font>

01:11:52.851 --> 01:11:54.269
Fergus.

01:11:55.479 --> 01:11:57.206
- Bear!
- <font color="#808080">(MOANING)</font>

01:11:57.231 --> 01:11:59.333
Dad!

01:11:59.358 --> 01:12:01.961
Count your stars, lass. It
almost had you. Are you hurt?

01:12:01.986 --> 01:12:03.754
It's your wife, Elinor.

01:12:03.779 --> 01:12:05.781
<font color="#808080">(ELINOR WHINING)</font>
<font color="#808080">(MEN SHOUTING)</font>

01:12:07.574 --> 01:12:08.993
Close the gate!

01:12:12.413 --> 01:12:14.556
- You're talking nonsense!
- It's the truth!

01:12:14.581 --> 01:12:17.851
There was a witch and she gave
me a spell. It's not Mor'du.

01:12:17.876 --> 01:12:20.354
Mor'du or not, I'll
avenge your mother!

01:12:20.379 --> 01:12:24.400
- I'll not risk losing you, too.
<font color="#0080FF">MERIDA</font>: - No, Dad! Just listen to me.

01:12:24.425 --> 01:12:27.111
Listen!
You can't!

01:12:27.136 --> 01:12:31.473
- It's your wife Elinor!
- Maudie, keep this and don't let her out.

01:12:31.598 --> 01:12:34.076
- What about the bear?
- Just stay put.

01:12:34.101 --> 01:12:35.436
<font color="#808080">(BARKING)</font>

01:12:36.812 --> 01:12:38.939
Oh...

01:12:42.026 --> 01:12:43.694
<font color="#808080">(YELLING)</font>

01:12:50.492 --> 01:12:51.994
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTING)</font>

01:12:56.707 --> 01:12:57.708
<font color="#808080">(STRAINING)</font>

01:13:00.044 --> 01:13:01.045
<font color="#808080">(FRUSTRATED GRUNT)</font>

01:13:01.295 --> 01:13:03.964
Come on, you sorry bunch
of galoots! Yeah!

01:13:12.848 --> 01:13:14.283
Mum!

01:13:14.308 --> 01:13:15.951
No.

01:13:15.976 --> 01:13:17.519
No. Mum.

01:13:20.522 --> 01:13:22.524
<font color="#808080">(WEEPING)</font>

01:13:35.537 --> 01:13:37.664
<font color="#808080">(GROANING)</font>

01:13:39.666 --> 01:13:41.143
Maudie. Maudie!

01:13:41.168 --> 01:13:43.854
I need you!

01:13:43.879 --> 01:13:45.339
Now!

01:13:48.342 --> 01:13:50.969
<font color="#808080">(MERIDA GASPS)</font>
Oh, no.

01:13:52.346 --> 01:13:54.264
Maudie.

01:13:57.184 --> 01:13:58.435
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>

01:13:59.978 --> 01:14:01.021
Get the key.

01:14:08.362 --> 01:14:09.630
<font color="#808080">(GROWLING)</font>

01:14:09.655 --> 01:14:12.032
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMING)</font>

01:14:16.703 --> 01:14:17.746
Yeah!

01:14:18.038 --> 01:14:20.207
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMING)</font>

01:14:21.208 --> 01:14:22.584
Oh, Maudie!

01:14:23.794 --> 01:14:24.795
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMING)</font>

01:14:27.381 --> 01:14:28.816
<font color="#808080">(BOTH SCREAMING)</font>

01:14:28.841 --> 01:14:31.385
Needle and thread. Needle and
thread. Needle and thread.

01:14:36.056 --> 01:14:37.391
<font color="#808080">(BARKING)</font>

01:14:39.893 --> 01:14:41.145
<font color="#808080">(HUFFING AND GASPING)</font>

01:14:44.064 --> 01:14:46.066
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTS AND MOANS)</font>

01:14:49.611 --> 01:14:51.296
There he goes!

01:14:51.321 --> 01:14:54.049
Needle and thread. Needle and
thread. Needle and thread.

01:14:54.074 --> 01:14:55.325
Ah, you beauty!

01:15:02.332 --> 01:15:04.351
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>

01:15:04.376 --> 01:15:06.128
<font color="#808080">(STRAINING)</font>

01:15:11.592 --> 01:15:13.177
<font color="#808080">(SHRIEKS)</font>

01:15:16.013 --> 01:15:17.931
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>

01:15:18.265 --> 01:15:19.641
<font color="#808080">(WHIMPERING)</font>

01:15:22.144 --> 01:15:25.355
One, two... Huh?

01:15:26.273 --> 01:15:27.316
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>

01:15:29.276 --> 01:15:31.128
<font color="#808080">(THUD)</font>
<font color="#0080FF">MAUDE</font>: - Oh!

01:15:31.153 --> 01:15:32.362
<font color="#808080">(CUB GROWLING)</font>

01:15:32.696 --> 01:15:33.697
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>

01:15:34.114 --> 01:15:35.115
<font color="#808080">(WHINING)</font>

01:15:51.465 --> 01:15:53.467
<font color="#808080">(CRIES OUT)</font>

01:15:54.676 --> 01:15:56.778
Steady, Hamish.

01:15:56.803 --> 01:15:58.805
<font color="#0080FF">FERGUS</font>: There he goes.

01:16:00.224 --> 01:16:02.893
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTS)</font>
<font color="#808080">(DOGS BARKING)</font>

01:16:04.686 --> 01:16:05.787
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

01:16:05.812 --> 01:16:07.522
<font color="#808080">(MEN SHOUTING IN DISTANCE)</font>

01:16:08.941 --> 01:16:10.943
<font color="#0080FF">FERGUS</font>: We've got his track!

01:16:11.568 --> 01:16:13.111
<font color="#808080">(BARKING)</font>
<font color="#808080">(MOANS)</font>

01:16:15.697 --> 01:16:17.866
- Back, back, back!
- Get him!

01:16:18.492 --> 01:16:20.492
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

01:16:21.787 --> 01:16:23.789
Angus!
Easy, laddie.

01:16:25.207 --> 01:16:26.917
<font color="#808080">(CRIES OUT)</font>

01:16:27.542 --> 01:16:29.169
Hubert, Harris, help Hamish.

01:16:29.395 --> 01:16:30.395
<font color="#808080">(SHOUTING)</font>

01:16:30.420 --> 01:16:33.020
<font color="#0080FF">FERGUS</font>: Watch your blade! You're
going to take somebody's arm off!

01:16:33.840 --> 01:16:35.175
Aye, we've got you now!

01:16:36.894 --> 01:16:39.655
<font color="#0080FF">FERGUS</font>: - Give me a hand over here!
- Put your back into it, Dingwall!

01:16:39.680 --> 01:16:40.864
<font color="#0080FF">LORD DINGWALL</font>: I'm doing
all the pulling here.

01:16:40.889 --> 01:16:42.569
<font color="#0080FF">LORD MACGUFFIN</font>: Down
you go, you scoundrel.

01:16:45.143 --> 01:16:47.104
<font color="#808080">(SQUEALS)</font>
Done!

01:16:47.938 --> 01:16:48.939
<font color="#808080">(WISP CALLS)</font>

01:16:50.148 --> 01:16:52.526
<font color="#808080">(HIGH-PITCHED CALLS)</font>

01:16:53.318 --> 01:16:55.028
Yeah!

01:16:57.656 --> 01:16:58.782
<font color="#808080">(GROWLS)</font>

01:17:00.742 --> 01:17:02.142
<font color="#808080">(ELINOR BEAR GROANS)</font>
<font color="#808080">(MEN SHOUTING)</font>

01:17:03.161 --> 01:17:04.621
<font color="#808080">(DOGS BARKING)</font>

01:17:05.038 --> 01:17:07.266
- Hah!
- <font color="#808080">(WHIMPERS)</font>

01:17:07.291 --> 01:17:08.850
<font color="#808080">(GROWLS)</font>

01:17:08.875 --> 01:17:10.377
<font color="#808080">(YELLS)</font>
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

01:17:10.669 --> 01:17:11.937
<font color="#808080">(MEN GASP IN SHOCK)</font>

01:17:11.962 --> 01:17:16.066
- Get back. That's my mother.
- Are you out of your mind, lass?

01:17:16.091 --> 01:17:18.260
- Mum, are you hurt?
- <font color="#808080">(MOANS)</font>

01:17:19.094 --> 01:17:20.404
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTS)</font>
<font color="#808080">(CRIES OUT)</font>

01:17:20.429 --> 01:17:21.905
<font color="#808080">(YELLS)</font>

01:17:21.930 --> 01:17:23.515
<font color="#808080">(YELLS)</font>

01:17:24.808 --> 01:17:25.851
Merida!

01:17:27.853 --> 01:17:31.273
<font color="#808080">(FERGUS GROANS)</font>
- <i>I'll</i> not let you kill my mother.

01:17:32.232 --> 01:17:33.959
<font color="#808080">(FERGUS SCREAMS)</font>
- Boys!

01:17:33.984 --> 01:17:35.711
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMING)</font>

01:17:35.736 --> 01:17:36.820
Boys?

01:17:37.821 --> 01:17:39.281
<font color="#808080">(HEAVY THUD)</font>

01:17:42.075 --> 01:17:43.427
<font color="#808080">(GROWLS)</font>

01:17:43.452 --> 01:17:45.178
- Mor'du!
- Kill it!

01:17:45.203 --> 01:17:47.456
<font color="#808080">(ALL YELLING)</font>
<font color="#808080">(ROARS)</font>

01:17:48.248 --> 01:17:49.891
<font color="#808080">(MEN SCREAMING)</font>

01:17:49.916 --> 01:17:51.918
You Scoundrel!

01:17:52.878 --> 01:17:53.879
<font color="#808080">(MEN GROANING)</font>

01:17:54.129 --> 01:17:55.129
<font color="#808080">(ROARS)</font>

01:17:55.380 --> 01:17:58.400
Come on! I'll take you
with my bare hands!

01:17:58.425 --> 01:17:59.634
<font color="#808080">(FERGUS GROANS)</font>

01:18:00.010 --> 01:18:01.778
<font color="#808080">(FERGUS CRIES OUT)</font>

01:18:01.803 --> 01:18:03.847
<font color="#808080">(ROARS)</font>

01:18:05.891 --> 01:18:06.950
<font color="#808080">(WHIMPERING)</font>

01:18:06.975 --> 01:18:08.435
<font color="#808080">(SNARLS)</font>

01:18:09.936 --> 01:18:11.079
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

01:18:11.104 --> 01:18:13.106
<font color="#808080">(ROARS)</font>

01:18:19.112 --> 01:18:20.112
<font color="#808080">(ELINOR BEAR MOANS)</font>

01:18:20.405 --> 01:18:21.823
<font color="#808080">(BOTH ROARING)</font>

01:18:32.417 --> 01:18:33.460
Mum!

01:18:34.711 --> 01:18:35.712
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

01:18:41.968 --> 01:18:43.887
<font color="#808080">(BOTH SNARLING)</font>

01:18:45.305 --> 01:18:46.640
<font color="#808080">(ELINOR CRIES OUT IN PAIN)</font>

01:18:49.267 --> 01:18:50.602
<font color="#808080">(STONE CRACKING)</font>

01:18:51.311 --> 01:18:53.313
<font color="#808080">(MERIDA SCREAMS)</font>

01:18:58.443 --> 01:18:59.986
<font color="#808080">(ROARING)</font>

01:19:05.867 --> 01:19:08.367
<font color="#808080">(CRACKING AND CRUMBLING)</font>

01:19:18.588 --> 01:19:19.588
<font color="#808080">(ROARS FEROCIOUSLY)</font>

01:19:20.173 --> 01:19:21.383
<font color="#808080">(SHRIEKS)</font>

01:19:43.029 --> 01:19:44.322
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>

01:19:49.494 --> 01:19:52.247
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>
The second sunrise.

01:19:56.877 --> 01:19:58.545
<font color="#808080">(STRAINING)</font>

01:20:00.213 --> 01:20:01.256
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTS)</font>

01:20:03.216 --> 01:20:04.926
<font color="#808080">(WHIMPERS)</font>

01:20:25.197 --> 01:20:26.531
<font color="#808080">(WHINES)</font>

01:20:31.578 --> 01:20:33.413
No...

01:20:35.165 --> 01:20:37.167
I don't understand.
I...

01:20:38.919 --> 01:20:40.921
<font color="#808080">(SNIFFLING)</font>

01:20:46.092 --> 01:20:47.594
<font color="#808080">(WEEPING)</font>

01:20:48.553 --> 01:20:52.140
Oh, Mum, I'm sorry.

01:20:54.100 --> 01:20:56.411
This is all my fault.

01:20:56.436 --> 01:20:58.438
I did this to you.

01:20:58.939 --> 01:21:00.440
To us.

01:21:01.358 --> 01:21:02.359
<font color="#808080">(SNIFFING)</font>

01:21:06.738 --> 01:21:08.740
You've always been there for me.

01:21:10.116 --> 01:21:12.118
You've never given up on me.

01:21:14.204 --> 01:21:15.872
I just want you back.

01:21:19.084 --> 01:21:21.086
<font color="#808080">(MERIDA SOBS)</font>

01:21:21.545 --> 01:21:23.547
I want you back, Mummy.

01:21:43.316 --> 01:21:45.318
I love you.

01:22:10.051 --> 01:22:11.653
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>

01:22:11.678 --> 01:22:13.029
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHS)</font>

01:22:13.054 --> 01:22:15.140
Mum!
You're back!

01:22:15.682 --> 01:22:17.225
<font color="#808080">(LAUGHING TEARFULLY)</font>

01:22:21.938 --> 01:22:23.331
You changed!

01:22:23.356 --> 01:22:24.941
Oh, darling,

01:22:26.192 --> 01:22:28.028
we both have.

01:22:29.195 --> 01:22:30.488
Elinor!

01:22:31.031 --> 01:22:32.924
